hadiths[161]{hadithnumber,text}:
2928,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabrdar ! tum mein se her shakhs muhafiz aur zimmedar hai aur her shakhs se uski raiyat ( jo koi aur jo kuch uski zimma daari mein hai) ke mutalliq puchha jaeyga . pas ameer , jo logon ka muhafiz hai, us se unke mutalliq puchha jaeyga . mard apney ghar walon ka muhafiz hai, us se unke mutalliq puchha jaeyga . aurat apney shohar ke ghar aur uskey bachon par muhafiz hai us se unke mutalliq puchha jaeyga , ghulam apney Malik ke maal ka muhafiz hai, us se us maal ke mutalliq puchha jaeyga . gharaz! tum sab ke sab raai aur haakim ho aur tum sab se tumhari raiyat ke mutalliq sawal kya jaeyga.''"
2929,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : ''aey Abdur-Rehman bin Samra! hukumat ka sawal na karna, kyonkey ye agar tumhen maangney par di gaee to tum is silsiley mein apney aap ke supurd kar diye jaogey, (yani Allah taala ki taraf se madad na hogi) lekin agar baghair maangney ke di gaee to us mein tumhari madad ki jaeygi .''"
2930,Hazrat Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main do aadmiyon ke sath Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua. pas un mein se eik ne ( baat kerney ke liye ( kalmaate-tashahud padhey aur phir kaha : ham aap ki khidmat mein hazir huey hain ke aap ham se apney kaam mein koi madad lein (yani aamil aur haakim bana den) aur doosrey ne bhi apney sathi ki si baat ki . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs ye zimme-daari talab karta hai wo hamarey nazdik sab se ziyada khaain hota hai. '' chunanche Abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazrat chahi aur kaha : mujhey maloom nahin tha ke ye kis maqsad se aaye hain. aur phir aapney apni wafat tak un se kisi kaam mein madad nahin li .
2931,Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat ibn Umme- Maktum (Raziallahu anhu) ko do baar Madiney ka wali banaya tha.
2932,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah taala jab kisi ameer ( haakim (ke sath khair ka irada farmata hai to usey koi mukhlis wazir inayat farma deta hai jo bhool janey par usey yaad dilaata hai aur yaad honey par uski madad karta hai, aur Allah jab uskey sath koi aur irada karta hai to uskey liye koi bura wazir bana deta hai jo bhool janey par usey yaad nahin dilaata aur yaad aaney par uski madad nahin karta.''"
2933,"Hazrat Miqdam bin Maadikarb (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uskey kandhey par haath maara, phir farmaya : ''aey Qudam! to kamiyab hua agar is haal mein faut hua ke na ameer bana, na uska secretery aur na Areef ( apni qom ka sardar.'' ("
2934,"ghalib qataan, eik shakhs se riwayat kartey hain, wo apney walid se wo apney dada se bayan kartey hain ke hamarey log eik chashmey par muqeem they. jab unko Islam ki dawat pahunchi, to pani ke us muntazim ne apni qom se kaha ke agar tum log Islam ley aao to main tumhen eik so oont dunga, chunanche unhoney Islam qubul kar liya aur phir usney un mein oont taqseem kar diye . phir usey khayal aaya ke ye oont un se wapis le-ley. to usney apney bete ko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja aur usey kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jaey aur unhen kahey ke mera walid aap ko salam kehta hai aur batana ke usney apni qom se kaha tha ke agar wo musalman ho jaeyn to wo unhen eik so oont dega , chunanche wo musalman ho gaey, to usney wo oont un mein baant diye . aur ab usey khayal aaya hai ke ye oont un se wapis le-ley to kya mera walid un oonton ka ziyada haqdaar hai ya wo log ? to agar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) haan kahen , ya nahin, to unhen arz karna ke mera walid bahut boodha hai aur wo apni qom ke pani ka Areef ( unka sardar ( hai. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) uskey baad ye mansab merey liye muqarrar farma den . chunanche uska beta aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha aur kaha : merey walid aap ko salam pesh kartey hain. aapney farmaya : ( وعليك وعلى أبيك السلام ( '' aur tum par aur tumharey walid par salam ho.'' phir usney kaha : merey walid ne apni qom se kaha tha ke agar wo musalman ho jaeyn to wo unhen so oont dengey , chunanche wo musalman ho gaey aur badey achey musalman Sabit huey .) jis par unhen oont dey diye gaey ( phir uska ( walid ka ( khayal hua hai ke ye oont un se wapis le-ley . kya wo ( mera walid ( unka ziyada haq daar hai ya wo log ? aapney farmaya : ''agar wo unhi ko dey dena chahta hai to theek hai aur agar wapis lena chahta hai to wo un oonton ka unki nisbat ziyada haqdaar hai. pas agar wo Islam laye hain to uska faeyda khud unhi ko hai aur agar Islam qubul nahin karengey to un se Islam ke liye qitaal kya jaeyga.'' ladkey ne phir kaha : mera baap bahut boodha hai aur wo pani ka muntazim hai) apni qom ka sardar hai) uski (yani merey walid ki) darkhast ye hai ke ye mansab ( Areef ( uskey baad aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) merey liye muqarrar farma den . aapney farmaya : '' Areef hona ( qom ka sardar banna ( haq hai aur logon ko Arfa se koi chaara bhi nahin, lekin ye Arfa ( sardar ( log jahannam mein janey waley hain. ''"
2935,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke '' السجل ( '' naami eik shakhs Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka kaatib tha.
2936,"Hazrat Raafe bin Khadij (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''haq ke sath sadqaat jama kerney wala aisey hai jaisey ke Mujahid fi sabeel Allah yahan tak ke wo ghar lot aaye.''"
2937,"Hazrat Aqba bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''changi aur bhatta leney wala jannat mein nahin jaeyga.''"
2938,Janab ibn Is-haq ne '' sahab maks'' ki wazahat mein kaha : us se murad wo shakhs hai jo (uski raah mein aaney janey waley tajiron aur doosrey logon se unke maal ka ( daswaan hissey leta ho.
2939,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ( jab wo zakhmi kiye gaey to unhen apna ja-nashin banaey janey ke mutalliq kaha gaya , to unhoney ( kaha : agar main ( apna ( ja-nashin na banaun to ( sahih hai) kyonkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ja-nashin nahin banaya tha aur agar bana jaun to bhi) durust hai) kyonkey Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ja-nashin bana gaey they. Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain : Allah ki qasam ! unhoney Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) hi ka naam liya aur mujhey yaqeen ho gaya ke wo Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke barabar kisi ko nahin samjhengey aur wo kisi ko khalifa muqarrar kerney waley nahin."
2940,Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sama aur itaat (sunney aur maanney) par baiat kartey they. (aap ke ehkam sunen gey aur b-khushi amal karengey (aur aap hamen talqin farmatey : '' un mein jin mein tum taqat rakho.''
2941,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke aurton se baiat leney ke baarey mein kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kabhi kisi ajnabi aurat ka haath nahin chhua , albatta ehad liya kartey they, aur jab wo ehad karti to aap usey farmatey : '' jao maine tum se baiat le li.''"
2942,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ke mutalliq aata hai ke unhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki sohbat ka sharf hasil hai. unki walida Zenab bint Humaid unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley gaeen aur arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool! us se baiat farma lein, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye chhota hai.'' aur aapney uskey sar par haath pher diya."
2943,"Hazrat Barida (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisey ham kisi kaam par mutayyan keren aur usey us par tankhwaah bhi den, to jo wo us se mazeed lega wo khayanat hogi.''"
2944,"Hazrat ibn Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain, Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey sadqaat ka aamil ( tehseeldar maal) banaya , jab main farigh ho kar aaya to aapney merey liye haq al-khidmat ada kerney ka hukm diya. maine arz kya : ye kaam maine Allah ki raza ke liye kya hai, aapney farmaya : jo milta hai le lo, maine bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke daur mein kuch kaam kya tha, to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey uska badal inayat farmaya tha."
2945,"Hazrat Mustaurid bin Shaddad (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''jo hamara aamil ho wo biwi hasil kar ley , agar uskey paas khaadim na ho to khaadim le-ley aur agar uskey paas rihaaish na ho to wo rihaaish hasil kar ley.'' mustaurid (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey bataya gaya hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi uskey ilawa ley to wo khaain hai ya chor .''"
2946,"Hazrat abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Azd qabiley ke eik shakhs ko sadqaat par aamil banaya jiska naam ibne-Lutbiya tha. . . . ibne-Sarah ne uska naam ibne-Lutbiya zikr kya hai. . . . jab wo wapis aaya to usney kaha : ye aap ka hai aur ye mujhey hadiya diya gaya hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) member par khadey huye, Allah ki hamd w sanaa bayan ki aur farmaya : '' aamil ko kya hua hai ke ham usey bhejtey hain phir wo aa kar kehta hai : ye aap ka hai aur ye mujhey hadiya diya gaya hai. wo apni maa ya baap ke ghar mein kyon na betha raha, phir dekhta ke usey hadiya milta hai ya nahin? tum mein se jo koi bhi is qism ki chiz lega wo usey qiyamat ke din lekar hazir hoga, agar wo oont hua to bil-bilaata aaeyga, agar gaaey hui to dakaarti hui aaeygi ya bakri hui to mimiyaati hui aaeygi.'' phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney dono haath buland farmaai yahan tak ke ham ne aap ki baghlon ki safedi dekhi. aapney farmaya : ''aey Allah ! maine yaqinan pahuncha diya. aey Allah ! maine yaqinan pahuncha diya. ''"
2947,"Hazrat abu-Masood Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey bator aamil bheja aur farmaya : ''aey abu-Masood ! jao aur khayal rakhna aisa na ho ke qiyamat ke din main tumhen paon ke tum aao aur tumhari peeth par sadqey ka koi oont bil-bilaata hua aaye , jisey tum ne khayanat se liya ho.'' kehtey hain ke) maine arz kya : agar maamla itna sakht hai) tab mein nahin jata . aapney farmaya : '' to main bhi tujhey majboor nahin karta.''"
2948,"Janab Abu-Maryam Azdi bayan kartey hain ke main Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) se milney gaya (jabke wo shaam mein hukmran they) to unhoney kaha : aey Abu-Fulaan ! kya khoob aaye ho (yani hamen tumharey aaney se khushi hui hai) aur ye jumla ( ما أنعمنا بك ( arab log bator istaqbal w khush aamadeed bola kartey hain. maine arz kya : eik hadees hai jo main aap ko bataaney aaya hun. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''Allah taala ne jis kisi ko musalmanon ke kisi maamley ka wali aur zimmedar bana diya ho, phir wo unki zarooriyat, hajat mandi aur faqeeri mein un se milney se gurez karey ( hijaab mein rahey ( tu Allah taala bhi us se hijaab farma lega, jabke wo zarurat mand hoga, mohtaj hoga aur faqir hoga.'' chunanche unhoney eik aadmi muqarrar kar diya jo logon ki zaruriyat aur haajaat un tak pahunchata tha."
2949,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen jo chiz bhi deta hun ya nahin deta , to uski wajeh ye hai ke main eik khazanchi ki tarah hun, chizon ko wahin rakhta hun jahan mujhey rakhney ka hukm diya gaya hai. ''"
2950,"Janab Malik bin Aus bin Hadsan (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke eik din Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne maale-fai ka zikr kya aur kaha : us maal ka main tum se ziyada haqdaar nahin hun aur na ham mein se koi eik kisi doosrey par ziyada haq rakhta hai, siwaye uskey ke ham Allah ki kitab ki ru se aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taqseem ke mutabiq apney-apney martabe par hain, ya to koi Islam qubul kerney mein sabqat kar chuka hai ya koi Islam ke liye apni bahaaduri ke jauhar dikhaney wala hai ya koi Ayaaldar hai ya koi hajatmand (lihaza un hi aitibaarat se ye maal taqseem kya jata hai. ("
2951,"Janab Zaid bin Aslam (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan gaey, unhoney puchha aey abu-Abdur-Rehman! (ye Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki kunniyat hai) aap kis zarurat se tashrif laey hain? unhoney kaha : aap azad shuda ghulamon (aur laundiyon) ka hissa ada karen. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko dekha hai ke aap ke paas jab bhi koi maal aata to aap (us mein sey) azad shuda ghulamon (aur laundiyon) ko pehley diya kartey they."
2952,"Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke) eik baar ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas eik thaili aai us mein naginey they, aapney unhen azad aurton aur laundiyon mein taqseem farma diya. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) kehti hain : merey walid azad aur ghulam sab mein taqseem kya kartey they."
2953,"Hazrat Auf bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jab maale-fai aa jata to aap usey isi din taqseem farma detey. aap biwi waley ko do hissey aur mujarrad ko eik hissey detey. ibne-musaffa ki riwayat mein mazeed ye alfaz bhi hain : hamen bhi bulaya gaya aur mujhey (Auf bin Malik ko) Ammar se pehley bulaya jata tha, mujhey bulaya aur do hissey inayat farmaey, kyonkey merey yahan biwi thi, phir merey baad Hazrat Ammar bin Yasir (Raziallahu anhu) ko bulaya gaya aur unhen eik hissey inayat farmaya."
2954,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farmaya kartey they : ''main mominon ke liye unki janon se bhi nazdik tar hun (ke mera maqam pahchaanein aur be-choon w chara itaat keren) chunanche jo koi maal chhod jaey to wo uskey ghar walon ka haq hai aur jo koi qarza chhod jaey ya chhotey bachey, to wo meri taraf hain aur merey zimmey hain. ''"
2955,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo maal chhod jaey to wo uskey warison ka hai aur jo parivar aur bachchey chhod jaey to wo hamari taraf hain.'' (ham unke zimmedar hain aur ham unki kafalat karengey.)"
2956,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) se manqul hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main her momin ke liye uski jaan se bhi qarib tar hun, jo shakhs faut ho jaey aur us par qarza ho to wo merey zimmey hai aur jo maal chhod jaey to wo uskey warison ka haq hai.''"
2957,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke unko ghazwa ahad ke din Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par pesh kya gaya jabkey unki umr chaudah saal thi , to aapney ijazat na di. aur phir ( agley saal ( khandaq ke moqe par pesh kya gaya jabkey us waqt unki umr pandarah saal thi, to aapney ijazat dey di."
2958,"Janab Sulaim bin Mateer ne kaha, mujh se merey walid Abu-Mateer ne bayan kya ke wo hajj ke liye rawana hua yahan tak ke jab maqam suweda mein pahuncha to maine dekha ke eik aadmi jo goya kisi dawaa ki talash mein hai ya rasoot dhoond raha hai, usney kaha : mujh se us shakhs ne bayan kya jisney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Hajjatil-wadaa mein suna tha jabkey aap logon ko waaz farma rahey they, kuch baaton ka hukm dey rahey they aur kuch se mana kar rahey they, aapney farmaya : '' logo ! ( baadshaahon ke) atiye aur hadiye jab tak atiye hon qubul kar saktey ho lekin jab Quraishi log hukumat ke liye ladney lagen aur ye hadiye tumharey deen ka iwaz bin jaeyn to chhod dena. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : us riwayat ko ibne-Mubarak ne b-waasta Muhammad bin Yasar, Sulaim bin Mateer se riwayat kya hai."
2959,"Sulaim bin Mateer ne apney walid se bayan kya aur ye Wadiyul-Qura ka rehney wala tha. uskey walid ne kaha : maine eik sahab se suna, wo kehtey they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Hajjatil-wadaa mein suna, aapney logon ko kuch ehkam bayan kiye aur kuch se mana farmaya , phir farmaya : ''aey Allah ! maine pahuncha diya ? .'' logon ne kaha : haan , aey Allah ! ( ham gawah hain ( phir aapney farmaya : ''jab ehle-Quraish aapas mein hukoomat ke liye jhagadney lagen aur atiye rishwat bin jaeyn to phir unhen chhod dena .'' puchha gaya ke ye bayan kerney wala kon hai? to logon ne kaha : ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sahabi zul-zawayd hain."
2960,"Janab Abdullah bin Kab bin Malik Ansari se riwayat hai ke Ansariyon ka eik lashkar apney ameer ke sath mein Iraan ke ilaqey mein gaya aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) her saal lashkaron ko baari baari bheja kartey they to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) deegar masroofiyaat ki wajeh sey) un se mashghool ho gaey (aur bhool gaey ( so jab muqarrara waqt guzar gaya to us janib ki sarhadon waley wapis chaley aaye to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne unko daanta aur dhamki bhi di, halanke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke as-haab they. unhoney kaha : Umar! tum ham se ghafil rahey ho aur hamarey baarey mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo hukm farmaya tha wo tum ne chhod diya hai ke mujahideen eik doosrey ke baad bari-bari se bhejey jaeyngey."
2961,"Janab Adi bin Adi Kandi ke sahibzadey ka bayan hai ke Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ne likha : jo shakhs ye puchey ke maale-fai kahan kahan kharch hota hai, to iska jawab ye hai ke unka musrif wohi hai jis ka Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) ne faisla kya tha aur ahle-eman ne bhi usey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman ki roshni mein adl par mabni paya tha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke baarey mein farmaya tha : ''Allah taala ne haq ko umr ki zaban aur dil par rakh diya hai.'' Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne maale-fai ke atiyon ko musalmanon ke liye khas kya hua tha aur dusrey mazhab walon ke liye aman w aman ka ehad diya tha b-ewaz us jiziya ke jo unse liya jata tha aur unka khums ya ghanimat mein koi hissey na tha."
2962,"Hazrat abu-Zar Ghifari (Raziallahu anhu) se manqul hai, kehtey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : ''bila-shuba Allah taala ne umr ki zaban par haq jari farma diya hai aur wo haq hi kehtey hain.''"
2963,"Hazrat Malik bin Aus bin Hadsan (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bula bheja, jabkey din chadh aaya tha, main unke paas aaya to dekha ke khuri chaarpai par bethey hain (us par koi bichona nahin tha) unhoney merey dakhil hotey hi kaha : aey malik! teri qom ke kuch log apney ehle w ayaal samet aahista aahista chaley merey paas pahunchey hain. maine unke liye kisi qadr maal ka keh diya hai to wo un mein taqseem kar do. maine kaha : agar aap ye kaam merey siwa kisi aur se keh den ( to behtar rahey .) unhoney kaha : tum hi usey lo . itney mein) unka khaadim ( Yarfa aa gaya, usney kaha : ameerul-momenin! Usman bin Affan, Abdur-Rehman bin Auf, Zuber bin Awam aur Saad bin abi Waqas (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) aap se milna chahtey hain. to unhoney kaha : haan, aur unke liye ijazat de-di aur wo andar aagey. Yarfa phir unke paas aaya aur kaha : ameerul-momenin! Abbas aur Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) aaye hain. aapney kaha : haan aur unke liye ijazat de-di to wo bhi andar aagey . Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : ameerul-momenin merey aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ke darmiyan faisla kar den."
2964,"Malik bin Aus (bin Hadsan) (Raziallahu anhu) ne ye waqia bayan kya, unhoney kaha : Hazrat Ali aur Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka us maal ke baarey mein jhagda tha jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko bano Nazir se bator Fai hasil hua tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne farmaya : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) chahtey they ke uskey baarey mein kisi bhi tarah taqseem ka naam na aaye."
2965,Hazrat Malik bin Aus bin hadsan (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kartey hain ke bano Nazeer ke amwaal wo they jo Allah taala ne apney Rasool ko baghair kisi ladaai ke) bator fai) diye they. musalmanon ne us par na ghodey dodaey they aur na oont . aur ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hi ke liye makhsus they. aap apney ehale-bait par kharch kartey they. (Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ke shekh) Ahmed bin Abda ne kaha : aap apney ehle ka eik saal ka kharch ley letey aur jo baqi bachta usko ghodon aur jihad fi sabeelillah ke saman mein laga detey. ibne-Abda ke alfaz they : ( في الكراع والسلاح ( (maani wohi hain jo ooper bayan huey hain.)
2966,"Janab Zohri (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sura hashr ki aayat : '' aur un ( logon (ka jo maal Allah taala ne apney Rasool ki taraf pher diya hai uskey liye tum ne koi ghodey aur oont nahin dodaey'' ke baarey mein farmatey hain : ye Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye khas hai. us mein uraina ki bastiyan, fidak waghera hain. (uskey baad saatwin aayat mein hai :) '' ladey bhide baghair bastiyon walon ka jo maal Allah taala ne apney Rasool ke tasarruf mein diya hai wo Allah, Rasool, qurbat daaron, yateemon, miskeenon, aur musafiron ka haq hai. '' (aur aagey aathwin aayat mein hai ke ye maale-fai) ''un fuqara muhajrin ka haq hai jo apney gharon aur maalon se nikal bahir kiye gaey . . . .'' (aur uskey baad ye bayan hua hai ke us maale-fai mein un logon ka bhi haq hai) jinhon ne un (muhajrin ki aamad) se pehley (Madiney mein) thikana bana liya tha aur emaan qubul kar liya tha. (ansaar Madina) aur) phir daswin aayat mein hai.'' aur wo log ( jo unke baad aaye . . . . '' ye ( aakhiri ( aayat tamam logon se mutalliq hai. aur musalmanon mein se koi bhi nahin bachta magar uska us fai mein hissey hai. . . . Ayub ne lafz '' ( haq ( '' ki bajaey '' ( حظ ( ''kaha . . . . siwaye tumharey kuch aisey logon ke jinki gardanon ke tum Malik ho. ( ghulam jo azad nahin huey aur unki puri zimmedari unke aaqaon par hai. ("
2967,"Hazrat Malik bin Aus bin Hadsaan (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Hazrat Ali aur Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ke beech faisla kartey huey) bator hujjat kaha tha : bano Nazeer, khaibar aur fidak ki zaminein (Allah ke hukm ke mutabiq) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye mukhtas thin. bano Nazeer wali jaaidaad dardnak haadson par kharch kerney ke liye hoti thi, fidak musafiron ke liye aur khaibar ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen hissey kar rakhey they, do hissey musalmanon mein aur eik hissey aap ke khandan ke ikhrajat ke liye tha. aap ke khandan ke kharch se jo bach jata aap usey muhajrin ke faqiron mein baant diya kartey they."
2968,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Rasool ki beti Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan kehla bheja ke usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke wirsey se hissey diya jaey jo aap bator fai Madina munawwara, fidak aur khaibar ke khums ka baqiya chhod gaey hain to Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya hai : ''hamara koi waris nahin hota, ham jo kuch chhod jaeyn wo sab sadqa hota hai, albatta aale-Muhammad ka kharcha (pehley ki tarah) is maal se pura kya jaeyga.'' aur Allah ki qasam! main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sadqe ko us haalat sey, jis par aap usey apni zindagi mein chhod gaey hain, tabdeel nahin kar sakta, main is par is tarah amal karunga jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kartey rahey hain. al-gharaz Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko us mein se kuch deney se inkar kar diya."
2969,"Urwa bin Zuber ne khabar di ke Nabi ki bivi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhen ye hadees bayan ki. is riwayat mein Urwa kehtey hain ke un dino (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ke baad) Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke us sadqey ka mutalba kya, jo aap Madina, fidak aur khaibar ke khums ka baqiya chhod gaey they. Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kya ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne jawab diya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka farman tha : ''hamara koi waris nahin hota, ham jo kuch bhi chhod jatey hain wo sadqa hota hai aur aale-Muhammad usi maal mein se khaeyngey.'' yani Allah ke maal mein se aur unhen haq nahin ke khaney peeney ke ikhrajat se ziyada lein."
2970,"Janab Urwa ne mujhey khabar di ke Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne unhen ye hadees bayan ki. Urwa ne is riwayat mein bayan kya ke Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne (Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko kuch deney sey) inkar kar diya aur kaha : jaisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kartey rahey hain, main us mein se kuch tark nahin karunga, agar maine aap ke tariqey mein se kuch bhi tark kar diya, to mujhey andesha hai ke kahin gumrah na ho jaun. albatta aap ka wo sadqa jo Madiney mein tha Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne usey Hazrat Ali aur Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki tauliyat mein dey diya, iskey baad is maamley mein Ali (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) par ghalib aagey they. khaibar aur fidak ko Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni nigrani mein rakha aur kaha : ye dono aap ka wo sadqa hain jo aap ke ittifaqi huqooq w ikhrajat ke liye they, unki tauliyat khalifa waqt ke haath mein hogi . chunanche wo aaj tak usi tarah hain."
2971,"Janab Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne aayate-karima : فما أوجفتم عليه من خيل ولا ركاب ''un par tum ne koi ghodey ya oont nahin dodaye.'' ki tafseer mein bayan kya ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehle-Fidak aur kaee bastiyon walon ke sath musaalihat farmaai thi, jabkey aap dusri bastiyon ka muhaasra kiye huey they, to un logon ne is beech mein suleh ka pegham bheja tha aur ye usi silsiley ka bayan hai ke فما أوجفتم عليه من خيل ولا ركاب yani baghair kisi jang w جدال ke ye hasil hui thi. Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : bano Nazeer ke amwaal Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye makhsus they ( kyonkey ( wo bator suleh ke Fateh huey they, usko quwat ke zor par hasil nahin kya gaya tha. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko muhajrin mein taqseem farma diya aur siwaye do ke kisi Ansari ko un mein se kuch nahin diya, ye do afrad bhi zarurat mand they."
2972,"Janab Mughira (bin Hakim Sanaani) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Hazrat umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) jab khalifa baney to unhoney bano Marwan ko jama kya aur kaha : fidak wali zameen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye khas thi, aap usi ki aamdani se apney ikhrajat purey kya kartey they, bano Hashim ke chhotey bachon par usi ke zariey se ehsan farmatey aur bewaaon ki shaadi karatey they. Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne uska mutalba kya ke ye usey dey diya jaey, to aapney inkar kar diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi mein ye maamla aisey hi raha yahan tak ke unki wafat ho gaee. phir Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa huey to us mein wo wohi kuch kartey rahey jaisey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi mein hota tha yahan tak ke apni raah chaley gaey ( wafat pa gaey .) phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) khalifa huey to us mein wohi kya jo wo dono kartey rahey they yahan tak ke wo ( bhi) apni raah chaley gaey ( unki bhi wafat ho gaee.) phir ye zameen Marwan ne apney liye khas kar li , phir umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ke qabzey mein aa gaee . umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : maine socha hai ke jo chiz Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( apni sahibzadi ( Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko nahin di hai, to mujhey bhi us par koi haq hasil nahin hai aur main tumhen gawah banata hun ke maine ye zaminein isi haal par wapas kar di hain jaisey ke thin. yani Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke zamaney mein. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : jab umr bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) khalifa baney to unki aamdani chaalis hazar Dinar thi aur jab wo faut huey to chaar so Dinar reh gaee thi agar wo zinda rehtey to aur bhi kam ho jati ."
2973,"Hazrat abu-Tufail (Aamir bin Waasila Lesi (Raziallahu anhu)) se marwi (bayan) hai ke Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke wirsey ka mutalba lekar Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas ayen , to unhoney kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''Allah taala jab apney Nabi ko koi rizq inayat farma deta hai, to uska sarparast wohi hota hai jo uskey baad) bator khalifa ( aaye .''"
2974,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mera wirsa dinaaron ki soorat mein taqseem nahin hoga. jo kuch bhi chhod jaun to wo biviyon ke ikhrajat aur ummal (governors) ki mehnat ke baad sab sadqa hoga.'' Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ( مؤنة عاملي ) ke maani hain ke wo afrad jo zameen par mehnat mazduri karen."
2975,"abul-Bakhtari kehtey hain ke maine eik aadmi se hadees suni jo mujhey pasand aai, maine kaha ke ye mujhey likh do, to usney ye mujhey saaf saaf likh di. ke Hazrat Abbas aur Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aaye jabki Talha, Zubair, Abdur-Rehman aur Saad (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) unke paas bethey huey they aur un dono ka aapas mein jhagda tha. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne Talha, Zubair, Abdur-Rehman aur Saad (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) se kaha : kya aap jantey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sab maal sadqa hota hai, siwaye uskey jo wo apney ghar walon ko khila den ya pehna den. ham log apna koi waris nahin banatey?'' un sab ne kaha ke haan. to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ghar walon par kharch kartey aur baqiya sadqa kar diya kartey they. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ho gaee aur Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) do saal tak us jaaidaad ke mutawalli rahey aur wohi kuch kartey rahey jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kartey they. phir (abul-Bakhtari ne ( Malik bin Aus ki hadees se kuch bayan kya."
2976,"ummul-momenin Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki jab wafat ho gaee to pak biviyon ne irada kya ke Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ko Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki khidmat mein bhejein taake wo unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki virasat se aathwan hissey inayat farma den, to Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) ne unse kaha : ''kya Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) farma nahin gaey : ''hamara koi waris nahin hota, ham jo kuch bhi chhod jaeyn, wo sadqa hota hai.''"
2977,"Janab ibne-Shahab ( Zohri ( (Rahimahullah) ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ki manind riwayat kya. us mein hai : maine kaha : kya tum Allah se nahin darti ho? kya tum ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ye farman nahin suna? aap farmatey they : '' hamara koi waris nahin hota, ham jo kuch chhod jaeyn wo sadqa hota hai aur ye maal aale-Muhammad ka hai jo unki mushkilon aur musibat zada afrad ke ikhrajat aur unke mehmano ke liye hai, jab main faut ho jaun to uska sarparast wohi hoga jo merey baad khalifa hoga .''"
2978,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) ka bayan hai ke mujh se Hazrat Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke main aur Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) khums ki taqseem ke silsiley mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baat kerney ke liye gaey jo aapney bano Hashim aur bano Muttalib ko hissey inayat farmaya tha. maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney hamarey bhaiyon bano Muttalib ko inayat farmaya hai magar hamen nahin diya, halanke hamari aur unki aap ke sath qurbat daari eik si hai, to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' bano Hashim aur bano Muttalib eik cheez hain.'' ( wajeh ooper darj hui ( Jubair (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khums mein se bano abd shams aur bano Nofal ka hissa na nikala jis tarah ke bano Hashim aur bano Muttalib ka nikala tha. raawi ka bayan hai ke Hazrat abu-Bakar Siddiq (Raziallahu anhu) khums usi tarah taqseem kya kartey they jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kartey they lekin wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke un qurbat daaron ko itna na detey they jitna Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) diya kartey they. chunanche Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke baad Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu) (bhi) unhen detey rahey ."
2979,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke hamen Hazrat Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano Abd Shams ya bano Nofal ko khums mein se kuch nahin diya jaisey ke bano Hashim aur bano Muttalib ko inayat farmaya. raawi ne kaha : Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) usi tarah khums taqseem kya kartey they jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) kartey they, magar wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qurbat daaron ko is tarah na detey they jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) detey they. jabkey Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) aur unke baad waley ( Hazrat Usman (Raziallahu anhu)) us mein se hissey diya kartey they."
2980,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke mujhey Hazrat Jubair bin Mut-im (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya , jab khaibar Fateh hua to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne '' qurbat daaron ke hissey ''main se bano Hashim aur bano Muttalib ko diya magar bano Nofal aur bano Abd Shams ko chhod diya. chunanche main aur Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir huey aur ham ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! bano Hashim ki fazilat ka hamen inkar nahin hai ke jo talluq aur maqam Allah taala ne aap ko unke sath diya hai so diya hai. magar hamarey bhai bano Muttalib , kya wajeh hai ke aapney unhen diya hai aur hamen chhod diya hai, halanke hamari (aap ke sath ( qurbat daari eik si hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' ham ( bano Hashim (aur bano Muttalib jahiliyat aur Islam mein juda juda nahin huey hain, ham aur wo eik cheez hain.'' aur aapney ( ye batatey huey ( apney haathon ki ungliyan eik dusri ke andar dalen ."
2981,"Hasan bin Saleh, Suddi (al-Kabir Ismael bin Abdur-Rehman bin abi kareema ( se naqal kartey hain ke '' ( ذي القربى ( '' se murad bano abdul-Muttalib hain."
2982,"Yazid bin Hurmuz ki riwayat hai ke jin dino main Hazrat ibne-Zubair (Raziallahu Anhuma) ko Shahid kya gaya Najda Haruri (ye khaarijiyon ka sardar tha) hajj ke liye aaya to usney Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se ( ذي القربى (ke hissey ke baarey mein puchhwaaya ke aap usey kis ka haq samajhtey hain? Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne farmaya : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke qurbat daaron ke liye hai jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen diya tha. aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne bhi us mein se hamen kuch pesh kya jisey ham ne apney haq se kam samjha , to ham ne usey unko wapis kar diya aur qubul kerney se inkar kar diya."
2983,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Laila (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey khums ke paanchwen hissey par wali banaya, pas maine usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki hayaat mubaarka mein uskey khas maqamat par kharch kya, aur phir Hazrat abu-Bakar aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) ki zindagi mein bhi usi tarah hota raha. phir kuch maal aaya to Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey bulaya aur farmaya : ley lo. maine kaha : mujhey uski zarurat nahin hai. unhoney kaha : ley lo, tum uskey ziyada haqdaar ho. maine kaha : ham us se be-niyaz hain. chunanche unhoney usko baitul-mal mein jama kar liya ."
2984,"Janab Abdur-Rehman bin abi-Laila (Rahimahullah) se marwi (bayan) hai ke maine Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo bayan kartey they ke main , Abbas , Fatima aur Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan ikhattey huey . maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool! agar aap munasib samjhen to kitabullah ke mutabiq jo khums mein hamara haq hai, aap apni zindagi mein mujhey uska wali bana den taake aap ke baad koi mujh se jhagda na karey. chunanche aapney aisey hi kar diya. phir main aapki hayaat mubaarka mein usey taqseem karta raha. phir Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujhey uska wali banaya. yahan tak ke jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ka aakhiri saal tha to unke paas bahut sa maal aaya, to unhoney mujhey us se hata diya. phir unhoney mujhey bula bheja, to maine arz kya : ab ke baras hamen uski zarurat nahin hai jabkey doosrey musalman uskey zarurat-mand hain, aap ye unhen de den. to unhoney usey musalmanon mein taqseem kar diya. phir Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke baad mujhey kisi ne uskey liye nahin bulaya. Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan se aaney ke baad main Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se mila to unhoney kaha : aey Ali! aaj tum ne hamen eik haq se mehrum kar diya hai jo aainda kabhi hamen nahin diya jaeyga . aur wo badey daana aadmi they."
2985,"Janab abdul-Muttalib bin Rabeea bin Haris bin abdul-Muttalib ne bayan kya ke uskey walid Rabeea bin Haris aur Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib ne abdul-Muttalib bin Rabeea (mujh sey) aur Fazal-bin Abbas se kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ja kar darkhast karo ke aey Allah ke Rasool! ham us umr ko pahunch gaey hain jo aap dekh rahey hain (bharpoor jawan hain) aur ham shadiyan karna chahtey hain aur aap aey Allah ke Rasool ! sab se badh kar husne-sulook aur sab se umda sila rehmi kerney waley hain, hamarey waliden ke paas hamarey haq mehar ke liye kuch nahin hai, to aap aey Allah ke Rasool! hamen sadqaat ka aamil bana dijiye , ham wohi karengey jo doosrey aamil kartey hain aur hamen hamara haq khidmat jo hoga mil jaeyga. abdul-Muttalib ne kaha : ham yehi guftgu kar rahey they ke Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) aa gaey, to unhoney kaha : Allah ki qasam! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tum mein se kisi ko sadqey par aamil nahin banaeyngey, to Rabeea ne un se kaha : ye tumhari baat hai ke tumhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki daamaadi mil gaee hai, hamen to us par tum se koi hasad nahin hai. phir Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne apni chadar bichhaai aur us par let gaey aur kehney lagey : main abul-Hasan hun aur maamla Faham bhi! (jaisey ke bada oont hota hai.) Allah ki qasam! main yahan se us waqt tak nahin jaunga jab tak ke tumharey sahibzadey jawab lekar nahin aa jatey, jis maqsad ke liye aapney unhen Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bheja hai. abdul-Muttalib kehtey hain : chunanche main aur fazal ( Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke darwazey ki taraf ( gaey . ham ne dekha ke Zohar ka waqt ho chuka hai aur jamaat khadi ho gaee hai to ham ne logon ke sath mil kar Namaz padhi . phir jaldi se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hujrey ke darwazey ke paas aagey . aap us din Hazrat Zenab binte-Jahash (Raziallahu anha) ke yahan they. ham darwazey ke paas khadey ho gaey yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tashrif ley aaye . pas aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( piyaar sey) merey aur fazal ke kaan pakad liye aur farmaya : '' nikalo jo tumharey ji mein hai. '' phir aap andar tashrif ley gaey aur hamen andar aaney ki ijazat di to ham andar chaley gaey. aur ham thodi der tak baat kerney ko eik doosrey par taaltey rahey (mein kehta ke tum baat karo wo kehta ke tum karo) bil-aakhir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se maine baat ki ya fazal ne . . . Abdullah bin Haris ko shak hai. . . aur hamarey baapon ne jo kaha tha ham ne aap ke gosh-guzar kar diya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik ghadi ke liye khamosh ho gaey. aapney apni nazar chhat ki taraf uthai hui thi. yahan tak ke bahut waqt guzar gaya aur aap hamen koi jawab nahin dey rahey they. yahan tak ke ham ne dekha ke ummul-momenin Zenab (Raziallahu anha) ne pardey ke peechey se hamen ishara kya yani jaldi mat karo, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumharey hi baarey mein fikr kar rahey hain. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apna sar jhukaya aur farmaya : ''ye sadqa to logon ka mail kuchail hai aur ye Muhammad aur aal Muhammad ke liye halal nahin hai. Nofal bin Haris ko merey paas bala lao.'' chunanche unhen bulaya gaya. aapney un se kaha : ''Nofal! abdul-Muttalib se (apni beti ka ( nikah kar do.'' chunanche Nofal ne merey sath ( apni beti ka ( nikah kar diya. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Mehmiya bin Juz ko bula lao.'' wo bano Zubeda mein se they. aur unko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khums ka nigraan banaya hua tha. aapney us se kaha : ''Mehmiya! fazal se ( apni beti ka ( nikah kar do.'' chunanche usney bhi kar diya. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us se farmaya : ''utho aur unhen khums mein se itna itna haq mehar ada kar do.'' Zohri kehtey hain ke Abdullah bin Haris ne mujhey uski miqdaar bayan nahin ki thi."
2986,"Hazrat Husain bin Ali (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Ali bin abi Talib (Raziallahu anhu) ne bataya ke merey paas eik achi oontni thi jo mujhey Badr ke moqe par ghanimat mein mili thi. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey us moqe par apney khums se bhi eik oontni inayat farmaai thi. jab maine irada kya ke (apni zauja) Fatima (Raziallahu anha) dukhtar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney ghar laun, to maine bano Qainuqa ke eik aadmi sey, jo ke sunaar tha wada liya ke wo merey sath chaley aur ham izkhir ghaas laeyn gey jisey mein sunaaron ko bech kar apney waleemey ka kharch bana sakoonga. pas us khayal se main apni oontniyon ke liye paalan, borey aur rassiyan waghera ikhattey kar raha tha, jabkey meri oontniyaan eik Ansari ke hujrey ke sath bethi hui thin. jab maine ye saman ikhatta kar liya aur aaya to dekha ke meri oontniyon ke kohan katey padey hain, unke pehlu cheer diye gaey hain aur jigar bhi nikal liye gaey hain. main ye manzar dekh kar apni aakhon par zabt na rakh saka (yani roney laga) aur puchha : ye kis ne kya hai? logon ne kaha : ye ( tumharey chacha) Hamza bin Abdul-Muttalib ne kya hai aur wo us ghar mein Ansariyon ke sath sharab ki eik majlis mein hain. eik gaaney wali ne unke aur unke sathiyon ke samney yun kaha : ألا ya حمز للشرف النواء ''aey Hamza ! sehan mein bethi un moti moti oontniyon ke dar pai ho.'' chunanche wo fauran uthey , apni talwaar li aur unke kohan kaat daley aur pehlu cheer diye aur jigar nikal liye . Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : phir main chala aaya yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahuncha . aap ke paas Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) bethey they. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujh par jo guzri thi usey meri soorat se bhaanp liya , to farmaya : ''kya hua ?'' maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! maine aaj jaisa din kabhi nahin dekha . Hamza ne meri oontniyon par hamla karkey unke kohan kaat daley hain aur pehlu cheer diye hain. aur wo us ghar mein mojud hai aur uskey sath doosrey sharab peeney waley bhi hain. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni chadar talab ki, usey odha aur chal padey . main aur Hazrat Zaid bin Harisa (Raziallahu anhu) unke peechey peechey they yahan tak ke aap us ghar ke paas aagey jis mein Hamza they. aapney andar janey ki ijazat talab ki, to aap ko bula liya gaya. aapney dekha ke sharab noshon ki majlis bapa hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Hamza ko uski karrawai par bura bhala kehney lagey aur wo nashay mein they. unki aankhen surkh ho rahi thin. Hamza ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf dekha phir nazar utha kar, aap ke ghutnon tak dekha. phir nazar uthai to naaf tak dekha. phir nazar uthai aur aap ke chehrey ko dekha. phir boley : tum merey baap ke ghulam honey ke siwa kya ho?'' tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne pehchaana ke ye nashey mein dhat hain, to aap ultey paon peechey palat aaye. aap nikley to ham bhi aap ke sath nikal aaye."
2987,"Hazrat Zuber bin Abdul-Muttalib ki saahibzadiyon Umme-Hakam ya zabaa (Raziallahu anha) mein se kisi eik ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas kuch qaidi aaye to main, merey behan aur Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) dukhtar Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aap ki khidmat mein hazir huin aur jis haal mein ham thin aap ke samney uska shikwa kya (ke sab kaam apney haath se kerney padtey hain. ( ham ne darkhast ki ke un qaidiyon mein se hamarey liye bhi kisi ka hukm dey diya jaey. to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Badr ke yateem (jinkey walid Badr mein Shahid huey) tum se pehley ley chukey hain, lekin main tumhen us se behtar amal batata hun ke her Namaz ke baad 33 baar Allahu-akbar, 33 baar subhanallah, 33 baar alhamdulillah aur (eik baar) لا إله إلا الله وحده لا شريك له له الملك وله الحمد وهو على كل شيء قدير (Allah ke siwa koi mabud nahin. wo eik akela hai, uska koi shareek sajhi nahin, hukumat usi ki hai aur tareef bhi usi ki hai aur wo her cheez par qudrat rakhney wala hai.) padha karo. Ayash (bin Aqba) ne kaha : ye dono khawatin Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki chacha zaad thin."
2988,"ibne-Aabud se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : kya main tumhen apni aur Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) dukhtar Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki baat na bataun aur Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko apney ehle mein sab se ziyada piyaar tha. maine kaha : haan bataiye. to unhoney kaha : Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) chakki chalaati thin yahan tak ke haathon par nishan pad gaey, pani ki mashk bhar kar laati thin yahan tak ke unke seeney par nishan pad gaey, ghar mein jhaado detin to kapdey kharab ho jatey. phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas londiyan aur ghulam aaye. maine un se kaha : agar aap apney walid ke paas ja kar kisi khaadim ke mutalliq kahen (to aap ko sahulat mil jaeygi.) chunanche wo ayen aur dekha ke kaee baaten kerney waley aap ke paas bethey hain, us par aap wapis aa gaeen. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) agley din unke paas aaye aur daryaft farmaya : ''kya kaam tha ?'' to wo khamosh rahen. maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! main bataey deta hun. ye chakki chalaati hain to inke haathon par nishan pad gaey hain. pani ki mashk utha kar laati hain to us se seeney par nishan pad gaey hain. aur ab aap ke paas londiyan ghulam aaye hain to maine un se kaha ke aap ki khidmat mein jaeyn aur koi khaadim talab kar lein jis se unhen un kamon ki mashaqqat mein aasani ho jaey. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Fatima! Allah se daro, apney rab ka fariza ada karo aur apney ghar walon ka kaam kaaj kya karo. aur raat ko jab soney lago to tentis baar (Subhanallah), tentis baar (alhamdulillah) aur chauntees baar (Allahu-akbar) keh liya karo, ye so baar hua. aur ye amal tumharey liye khaadim se badh kar hai.'' Hazrat Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : main Allah azz-w-jall se aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se (dil w jaan se) razi hun."
2989,Imam Zohri (Rahimahullah) ne b-waasta Ali bin Husain (Rahimahullah) ye qissa bayan kya hai. aur kaha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sayeda Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ko koi khaadim nahin diya tha.
2990,"mujja-aa (bin Muraara Hanfi Yamami (Raziallahu anhu)) se marwi (bayan) hai ke wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur apney bhai ki diyat talab ki jisey bano zehal ki shaakh bano sudoos ke logon ne qatl kar diya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''agar main kisi mushrik ki diyat deta hota to terey bhai ki bhi dey deta. taaham mein tujhey uska badla dunga.'' pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey likh diya ke sab se pehla khums jo bano zehal ke mushrikon se hasil hoga us mein se usko eik so oont diye jaeyngey . chunanche uska eik hissey usney hasil kar liya uskey baad phir banu-zehal musalman ho gaey. to Mujja-aa ne baqi maanda ka mutalba Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) se kya aur unko Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tehreer pesh kar di. chunanche Hazrat abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne uskey liye Yamaama ke sadqe se baara hazar saa likh diye, chaar hazar saa gehun, chaar hazar saa jau aur chaar hazar saa khajoor. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wo tehreer jo aapney mujja-aa ko likh kar di thi uska mazmoon ye tha : '' Bismillahir-rehmanir-rahim : ye tehreer Muhammad Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki janib se bano Salma ke mujja-aa bin Murara ke liye likhi gaee hai ke maine usey uskey (maqtool) bhai ke iwaz main eik so oont ata kiye hain, jo ke bano Zehal ke mushrekin se hasil honey waley pehley khums mein se ada kar diye jaeyngey.''"
2991,Aamir Shobi (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka ghanimat main eik khas hissey hua karta tha jisey (Safee) kaha jata tha. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam)) chahtey to ghulam ley letey ya londi ya ghoda (aur ye) khums nikalney se pehley ley saktey they.
2992,ibn Aun kehtey hain ke maine Muhammad bin Sirin (Rahimahullah) se Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hissey aur) Safee (ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) chahey kisi jihad mein shareek na bhi hotey aap ka hissa nikala jata tha aur khums mein se sab se pehley aap ke liye koi khas chiz nikal li jati thi aur usey (Safee) kaha jata tha.
2993,"Janab Qatada (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab kisi ghazwey mein shareek hotey to aap ka eik khas hissey ( Safee ( hota tha aap jo chahtey ley saktey they. chunanche Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ( ummul-momenin ( usi hissey mein se thin , aur jab aap khud shareek na hotey to aap ka hissa rakha jata tha, magar wo aap se muntakhab na karaya jata ."
2994,Hazrat Aaysha (Raziallahu anha) (ummul-momenin) ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) (ummul-momenin) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hissey (Safee) mein aai thin .
2995,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke ham khaibar aaye . jab Allah taala ne qila Fateh kara diya to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke samney Safiya bint Huyi ke Husn w jamaal ka tazkira hua, unka shohar qatl ho gaya tha jabkey wo abhi dulhan thin. pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen (unke sadmey ke izaaley aur muaashrey mein ooncha maqam deney ke liye) apney liye muntakhab farma liya. aap usey lekar rawana huey yahan tak ke jab ham sadde-Sehba ke maqam par pahunchey to wo halal ( haiz se paak) ho gaeen to aapney unke sath shabe-Zufaaf guzari."
2996,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Safiya (Raziallahu anha) ko pehley Dahiya kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) ne chuna tha magar baad mein) unke purey halaat gosh-guzar kiye janey ke baad) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke hissey mein aa gaeen .
2997,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Hazrat Dahiya kalbi (Raziallahu anhu) ke hissey main eik bahut hi khoobsurat londi aai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko saat ghulam de-kar kharida liya. phir aapney usey umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anha) ke hawaley kya taake usey banaeyn sanwaarein aur bator dulhan tayyar karen. Hammad kehtey hain aur mera khayal hai ke aapney farmaya : ye umme-Sulaim ke yahan iddat puri kar ley aur ye Safiya bint Huyi thin."
2998,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke khaibar mein qaidiyon ko jama kya gaya , to Hazrat Dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! mujhey qaidiyon mein se eik londi inayat farma den . aapney farmaya : '' jao aur eik londi ley lo .'' '' to unhoney Safiya binte-Huyi ko chun liya . phir eik aadmi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! aapney Safiya binte-Huyi ko Hazrat Dahiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke hawaley kar diya hai. wo Qureza aur Nazeer (yahudi qabeelon) ki sardar hai (sardar ki beti hai) ye sirf aap hi ke zeba hai. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' Dahiya ko bulao .'' usey lekar aaye. jab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Safiya ko dekha to Dahiya se farmaya : ''qaidiyon mein se uskey ilawa koi aur londi ley lo.'' chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey azad kar diya aur phir us se nikah kar liya ."
2999,"Janab Yazid bin Abdullah (bin Shikhkhir) bayan kartey hain ke ham (Basra ke mohalley) Marbad mein they ke eik shakhs aaya . uskey sar ke baal bikhrey huey they aur wo haath mein surkh chamdey ka eik tukda liye huey tha. ham ne kaha : tum goya dehat ke rehney waley ho? usney kaha : haan. hamne kaha : ye terey haath mein chamdey ka tukda kaisa hai, zara hamen dikhao? wo usney hamen dey diya. ham ne usey padha to usmein tehreer tha : ''Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se bani Zuhair bin Aqeesh ke liye . tum log agar (La-ilaah-illallah Muhammad Rasulullah) ki shahadat do, Namaz qaaim karo, Zakat ada karo, ghanimat mein se paanchwan hissey (khums) aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka hissa khas ( Safee ( ada karo, tu Allah aur uskey Rasool ki aman se aman mein ho.'' ham ne puchha : tumhen ye tehreer kis ne di hai? usney kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ."
3000,"Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah bin Kab bin Malik (kuch nuskhon mein Abdur-Rehman bin Abdullah ki bajaey Abdur-Rehman bin Kab hai aur yehi sahih hai. kyonkey Abdur-Rehman ( apney walid se riwayat kartey hain yani Hazrat Kab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se. aur wo un teen afrad mein se they jinki tauba qubul ki gaee thi. bayan kya ke) yahudiyon ka sardar ( Kab bin Ashraf, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki bahut badgoi kya karta tha aur kuffar Quraish ko un par hamla aawar honey ki targheeb bhi deta rehta tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab Madina tashrif laye to shehar walon mein teen tarah ke log bastey they, yani musalman, mushrik but-parast aur yahood. aur ye yahudi, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur aap ke as-haab ko bahut aziyat diya kartey they. tu Allah azz-w-jall ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko sabr aur darguzar ka hukm diya. aur unhi ke silsiley mein ye aayat utri : (ولتسمعن من الذين أوتوا الكتاب من قبلكم . . ۔ ) '' aur ye bhi yaqeeni hai ke tumhen un logon ki taraf sey, jinhen tum se pehley kitab di gaee hai aur mushrikon ki taraf sey, bahut si dukh deney wali baaten sunni padengi, aur agar tum sabr kar lo aur perhezgari ikhtiyar karo to yaqinan ye badi himmat ka kaam hai. ''aur jab Kab bin ashraf (yahudi) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aziyat deney se baaz na aaya to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (raees Aus) Hazrat Saad bin Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya ke koi jamaat bhej do jo uska kaam tamam kar dey . chunanche unhoney Hazrat Muhammad bin Muslima (Raziallahu anhu) ko bhej diya. aur phir uskey qatl ka qissa bayan kya. jab un logon ne usko qatl kar diya to yahudi aur mushrik ghabra gaey aur subh ke waqt Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur kaha : hamarey sahab ko raat ke andherey mein qatl kar diya gaya hai. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unko, jo-jo wo kaha karta tha, sab bataya aur unhen dawat di ke aao hamarey tumharey darmiyan eik tehreeri muahida ho jaey jis par sab ka ittifaq ho. chunanche Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney aur yahudiyon aur tamam musalmanon ke beech eik tehreer likh li (yani muahida ho gaya.)"
3001,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Badr ke moqe par jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Quraish par ghalib aagey aur Fateh ke baad Madina pahunchey to yahudiyon ko bano Qainuqaa ke baazar mein jama kya aur farmaya : ''aey jamaat yahood! Islam qubul kar lo, qabl uskey ke tumhen un halaat se do-chaar hona padey jin sey Quraishi do chaar huey hain.'' to un logon ne kaha : aey Muhammad! aap dhokey mein na rahen ke Quraish ke anaadi logon ko qatl kar aaye hain, wo jang karna jantey hi nahin they. agar tum ne ham se jang ki to pata chal jaeyga ke ham mard hain, tumhara ham jaison se samna nahin hua hai. chunanche Allah taala ne ye aayat utaari : ( قل للذين كفروا ستغلبون‏ ( '' kafiron se keh dijiye ke tum an-qareeb maghloob kiye jao gey.'' raawi hadees musrif (bin Amr) ne aagey tak padha : (فئة تقاتل في سبيل الله ، وأخرى كافرة) '' eik jamaat tu Allah ki raah mein lad rahi thi (Badr mein) aur doosra giroh kafiron ka tha. ''"
3002,"Hazrat Muhaisa (ibne-Masood bin Kab Ansari khazraji) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya .'' jis yahudi par bhi tumhara bas chaley usey qatl kar dalo.'' chunanche Muhaisa ne eik yahudi tajir par, jiska naam shabeeh tha, hamla kya aur usey qatl kar dala jo unke sath rehta tha aur (Muhaisa ka bhai) Huwesa abhi un dino musalman nahin hua tha aur umr mein Muhaisa se bada tha. jab usney qatl kar diya to Huwesa, mahiisa ko maarney laga aur kehta tha : aey Allah ke dushman! qasam Allah ki ! terey pet ki bahut si charbi usi ke maal ki wajeh se hai (yani wo tera Mohsin hai aur to ney usko qatl kar dala hai.)"
3003,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai ke ham log masjid mein bethey huey they ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hamarey paas tashrif laye aur farmaya : ''chalo utho yahudiyon ki taraf chalo.'' chunanche ham aap ke sath mein chaltey huey unke paas pahunchey. phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ruk gaey aur unhen pukara aur farmaya : ''aey jamaat yahood! Islam qubul kar lo! aman mein rahogey .'' unhoney kaha : abul-Qaasim! aapney pegham pahuncha diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne phir farmaya : ''Islam qubul kar lo! salamti mein rahogey.'' unhoney kaha : abul-Qaasim! aapney pegham pahuncha diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main yehi chahta hun (ke tum iqrar kar lo ke maine pegham pahuncha diya hai.'' ( aapney teesri baar farmaya : ''yaad rakho! zameen Allah ki hai, aur uskey Rasool ki aur main tumhen us zameen se jala watan kerney wala hun. jisey apney maal mein se kuch milta ho to wo usey bech ley , warna yaad rakho ! zameen Allah ki hai aur uskey Rasool ki .''"
3004,"Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Kab bin Malik Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke eik sahabi ke wastey se bayan kartey hain ke Quraish Makka ne Abdullah bin Ubai ( munafiq (aur uskey ham-nawa (sathi) Aus w khazraj ke doosrey but-parast logon ko khat likha, jabkey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) Madina munawwara tashrif la chukey they aur ye Badr se pehley ka waqia hai. unhoney likha ke tum logon ne hamarey aadmi ko panah dey rakhi hai aur ham Allah ki qasam kha kar kehtey hain ke tum log us se jang karo ya usey (apney yahan sey) nikal bahir karo, warna ham sab mil kar tum par dhaawa bolengey yahan tak ke tumharey jawaanon ko qatl kar dengey aur tumhari aurton ko apney qabzey mein ley aaeyngey. ye khat jab Abdullah bin Ubai aur uskey sathi but-paraston ko pahuncha to wo log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jang ke liye ikhattey ho gaey. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko jab ye khabar pahunchi to aapney un se mulaqat ki aur farmaya : ''Quraish ki dhamki se tum log bahut ziyada mutassir ho gaey ho aur wo tumhara usse ziyada nuqsan nahin kar saktey jitna ke tum apney haathon khud kar bethna chahtey ho. kya tum apney beton aur apney bhaiyon se qitaal karna chahtey ho ?'' jab unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se ye baat suni (aur uski haqeeqat ko samajh gaey) to wo titar-bitar ho gaey. kuffar Quraish ko ye khabar mili to unhoney waqia Badr ke baad yahudiyon ko likha ke tum log aslaha aur qilon ke Malik ho. tum log ya to laaziman hamarey aadmi se jang karo warna ham aisey aur aisey karengey aur phir hamarey aur tumhari aurton ki paazebon ke darmiyan koi haael na ho sakega (yani ham mardon ko qatl kar dengey aur aurton ko londiyan bana lengey.) jab unke likhey ki khabar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas pahunch gaee to is beech mein bano nazir ne bhi (Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey) dhoka kerney ka qasad kya. unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kehla bheja ke aap apney tees as-haab ke sath hamari taraf ayen aur ham mein se tees aalim ayen aur eik darmiyani jagah mein milen. ye log aap ki baat sunen, agar unhoney aap ki tasdeeq ki aur aap par emaan ley aaye to ham bhi aap par emaan ley aaeyngey. pas Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne (logon ko) unki khabar bata di. jab aglaa din hua, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) lashkar lekar gaey aur unka gheraw kar liya aur unse kaha : ''Allah ki qasam! tum logon par mujhey koi aitimaad nahin siwaey iske ke eik (naey) ehad ke zariey se jo tum ( naey sirey sey) merey sath karo.'' un logon ne ehad w paimaan deney se inkar kar diya. to aapney us din un se qitaal kya. phir agley din lashkar lekar un banu Qureza par chadhai ki aur bano Nazeer ko chhod diya. aapney un (banu Qureza) se mutalba kya ke wo (naey sirey sey) ehad w paimaan karen, unhoney muahida kar liya . aur aapney un se tawajjoh hataai. aur (agley din dobara) bano Nazeer par lashkar lekar chadhai ki aur un se qitaal kya yahan tak ke wo jala watni par razi ho gaey. chunanche bano Nazeer jala watan ho gaey, aur jo wo utha saktey they ghar ka asbab, gharon ke darwazay, shehteer aur kadiyan waghera oonton par laad lein. chunanche bano Nazeer ki khajuren bator khas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki tahweel mein aa gaeen. Allah ne wo aap ko inayat farmaeyn. aur aap ke liye makhsus kar den. Allah taala ne farmaya : (وما أفاء الله على رسوله منهم فما أوجفتم عليه من خيل ولا ركاب) ''aur Allah ne un mein se jo kuch apney Rasool ko dlwaya hai tum ne us par koi ghodey ya oont nahin dodaey ( baghair qitaal ke hasil hua hai.'') '' Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne uska aksar hissey muhajrin mein taqseem farma diya aur Ansariyon mein se sirf do aadmiyon ko diya jo hajat mand they, unke ilawa kisi Ansari ko kuch nahin diya. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sadqe mein se yehi baqi hai jo bano Fatima (Raziallahu anha) ke qabzey mein hai."
3005,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke bano Nazeer aur Qureza ke yahudiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se jang ki) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khilaf sazishen kin ( to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano Nazeer ko Madina se nikal bahir kya aur Qureza ko unke gharon mein rehney diya aur un par ehsan farmaya. yahan tak ke Qureza ne baad mein jang ki) ghazwa ehzaab ke moqe par kiye gaey muahidey ki khilaf warzi ki aur dhoka diya ( to unke jangju mard qatl kar diye gaey aur unki aurton , bachon aur amwaal ko musalmanon mein taqseem kar diya gaya, siwaye un baaz logon ke jo (karawai se pehley) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se aa miley they to aapney unko aman di aur wo Islam ley aaye (aur qatl se bach gaey ). Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne banu-Qenuqa aur bano Harisa ke sab yahudiyon ko jo Madina mein reh rahey they bahir nikal diya. bano Qenuqaa Hazrat Abdullah bin Salam (Raziallahu anhu) ki qom thi."
3006,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehle khaibar se jang ki, unki khajuren aur zameenein aap ke qabzey mein aa gaeen aur unhen apney qiley mein mahsoor ho janey par majboor kar diya gaya. to unhoney aap se musaalihat kar li ke tamam zard w safed ( sona chaandi (aur aslaha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye hoga aur deegar asbab jo unke oont utha saken utha ley jaeyngey aur koi chiz chupaeyn gey nahin aur na ghayeb karengey . agar aisa kya to unke liye koi zimma aur ehad na rahega . magar unhoney chamdey ka eik boraa ghayeb kar diya jo Huyi bin Akhtab ka tha aur wo khud khaibar se pehley qatl ho gaya tha. wo ye boraa bano Nazeer ke Madina se jala watan kiye janey ke moqe par utha kar laya tha, us borey mein un logon ke zewraat they. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Sa-ya ( yahudi ( se kaha : '' Huyi bin Akhtab ka bora kahan hai? '' usney kaha : wo jangon mein aur doosrey ikhrajat mein kharch ho gaya hai. magar Sahaba ne usey dhoond nikala. tab ibne-abi Haqiq ko qatl kya gaya, unki aurton aur bachon ko qaidi bana liya gaya aur unhen wahan se jala watan kerney ka irada kar liya, to unhoney kaha : aey Muhammad! hamen yahan rehney den ham us zameen mein mehnat karengey aur jab tak aap (hamen rakhna) chahengey uski aamdani ka aadha ham lengey aur aadha aap ko dengey. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (us pedawar mein sey) apni biwiyon mein se her eik ko usi ( 80) wasq khajoor aur bees ( 20 ( wasq jau diya kartey they."
3007,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : logo be-shak Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ke yahudiyon se ye tey kya tha ke jab ham chahengey unhen nikal bahir karengey. to jisney un se kuch lena ho wo wasul kar ley, mein yahudiyon ko nikaalney laga hun. chunanche uskey baad unhoney unko nikal diya."
3008,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke jab khaibar Fateh ho gaya to yahudiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se darkhast ki ke hamen yahin rehney diya jaey. ham mehnat karengey aur jo aamdani hogi us se aadhi aap ko ada karengey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''main tumhen us shart par yahan rehney deta hun ke jab tak ham chahengey.'' chunanche wo usi ke mutabiq wahan rahey. aur khaibar se hasil honey wali aadhi khajoor kaee hisson par taqseem ki jati thi aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) paanchwan hissey liya kartey they. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni biwiyon mein se her biwi ko so wasq khajoor aur bees wasq jo inayat farmaya kartey they. jab Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne yahudiyon ko nikalney ka irada kya to azwaaj Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se kehla bheja ke aap mein se jis ka ji chahey mein usey itney darkht diye deta hun jis se so wasq khajoor hasil ho aur wo darkht, zameen aur pani usi ka hoga. aur aisey hi is qadr zameen diye deta hun jis se bees wasq jo hasil hon. aur jo pasand karey ham khums mein se uska hissey pehley ki tarah ada kartey rahengey ."
3009,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar par chadhai ki. so ham ne usey qehar w quwat se hasil kya aur qaidi ikhattey kiye.
3010,Hazrat Sehal bin abi Hasma (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ko do hisson mein taqseem kya. eik hissey aap ke ittifaqi ikhrajat aur zati zarooriyaat ke liye khas tha aur aadha musalmanon ke liye . aapney usey un mein atthaara hisson mein taqseem kya tha.
3011,"Janab Bashir bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke unhoney as-haab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki eik jamaat se suna, unhoney bayan kya, aur yehi hadees zikr ki : chunanche aadhey hissey musalmanon ke they un mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka hissa bhi tha aur baqi aadhey musalmanon ki ittifaqi zaruriyat aur mushkilon ke liye alehda kar liye ."
3012,"Janab Bashir bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) jo ke ansar ke maula they, kaee as-haab Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab khaibar Fateh kya to usko kul chhattis hisson par taqseem kya, aur her hissey mein so hissey they. chunanche us mein se aadhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur musalmanon ke liye they. aur baqi aadhey ittifaqi ikhrajat ke liye mehfooz rakhey gaey ke aap ke paas wufood aatey they ya koi hangami kharch hota ya musalmanon par koi mushkil aa padti (to us mudd mein se liya jata tha.)"
3013,"Janab Bashir bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke jab Allah taala ne apney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khaibar inayat farma diya to aapney usey chhattis hisson par taqseem kya. her hissey mein so hissey they. chunanche un mein se aadhey aap ke ittifaqi ikhrajat aur aap ke paas aaney waley mehmano aur wufood ke liye they yani qila watiha, kutaiba aur unke sath mulhiq zaminon waghera aur baqi aadhey musalmanon mein taqseem kar diye , yani qila shaqq aur Natah aur unke muzaafat. aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka hissa bhi unhi ke aas-paas mein tha."
3014,Janab Bashir bin Yasar (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Allah taala ne jab apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko khaibar inayat farma diya to aapney usey kul chhattis hisson mein taqseem farmaya. aapney aadhey yani atthaara hissey musalmanon ke liye khas kar diye . her hissey so hisson par mushtamil tha aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi unke sath shareek they. aap ka hissa bhi usi tarah tha jaisey ke eik aam musalman ka . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne atthaara hissey apney aadey waqton aur musalmanon ki hangaami zarurat ke liye alehda kar diye they aur ye they qila wateeh aur kutaiba ( eik basti (aur Sulalim aur unke aas-paas. jab ye zameenein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) aur musalmanon ke qabzey mein aa gaeen to aap ke paas koi aisey mehnat kash na they jo unke bajaey kaam kartey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne yahudiyon ko dawat di aur unse maamla tey kar liya.
3015,"Hazrat Majmaa bin Jariya Ansari (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, . . . aur ye un haafizon mein se they jinhen pura Quran yaad tha. . . . . bayan kartey hain ke khaibar ko un mujahideen mein taqseem kya gaya jo Hudebiya mein shareek they. pas Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey atthaara hisson par taqseem kya tha. us lashkar ki tadaad eik hazar paanch so thi. un mein se teen so ghud-sawar they, chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ghud-sawar ko do hissey diye aur pedal ko eik hissa."
3016,"Janab Zohri, aur Abdullah bin abi Bakr se aur Muhammad bin Muslima ke baaz saahibzadgan se riwayat hai ke ehle-khaibar ke kuch log bach gaey to wo qila band ho gaey. aur unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se darkhast ki ke hamarey khoon maaf kar diye jaeyn (yani qatl na kya jaey) aur hamen yahan se nikal janey ka moqa diya jaey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey qubul farma liya. ehale-Fidak ne ye maamla suna to wo bhi is baat par razi ho gaey. chunanche ye qiley aur zameenein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke liye makhsus rahen, kyonkey un par koi ghodey aur oont nahin dodaey gaey they (jang nahin hui thi.)"
3017,"Janab Saeed bin Musaiyab (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ka kuch hissey quwat se (jang karkey) Fateh kya tha. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne b-sanad Haris bin miskeen, ibne-Shahab Zohri se riwayat kya ke khaibar ka kuch hissey jang se aur kuch suleh se hasil hua tha. kutaiba ( ki basti aur zameen (ka aksar hissey quwat ( jang ( se hasil hua tha aur us mein kuch hissey musaalihat ka bhi tha. ( ibne-Wahab kehtey hain ( maine Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) se puchha : kutaiba kya hai? to unhoney kaha : ye khaibar ki zameen hai us mein khajuron ke chaalis hazar darkht they."
3018,ibne-Shahab Zohri (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ko qitaal karkey bazor quwat Fateh kya tha. aur qitaal ke baad uskey kuch logon ne ye ilaaqa chhod deney ki shart par apni qila bandi ko khatam kya (aur suleh kar li.)
3019,"Janab ibne-Shahab Zohri (Rahimahullah) ki riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ka khums nikala phir is sab ko ehale Hudebiya par baant diya, chahey (chahe) koi hazir tha ya ghair hazir."
3020,"Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : agar mujhey baad mein aaney waley musalmanon ka khayal na ho, to jo basti bhi Fateh ho main usey taqseem kar dun jaisey ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne khaibar ko taqseem kiya tha."
3021,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ka bayan hai ke Fateh Makka ke moqe par Hazrat Abbas bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu), Abu-Sufiyaan bin Harab ko Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein ley aaye , chunanche unhoney marruz-zohraan ke maqam par Islam qubul kar liya. Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Abu-Sufiyaan aisa aadmi hai jisey fakhr aur badai pasand hai, agar aap uskey liye koi chiz khas farma den to ( munasib hoga). aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''haan, jo shakhs Abu-Sufiyaan ke ghar mein dakhil ho jaey usey aman hai aur jo apney ghar mein darwaza band karkey baithey rahey wo aman mein hai.''"
3022,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab marruz-zohraan ke maqam par padaaw dala , to Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam ! agar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apni quwwat ke zor par Makka mein dakhil ho gaey aur is se pehley ehle-Makka aap ke paas na aaye aur aman na maangi to is mein Quraish ki bahut badi halakat hai, chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke khachchar par baith kar bahir nikla , maine socha shayad mujhey koi shakhs mil jaey jo kisi kaam se nikla ho to wo ehle-Makka ke paas jaey, unhen Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki aamad ke mutalliq khabrdar kar dey aur wo aap ki khidmat mein hazir ho jaeyn aur aman talab kar lein. chunanche main chala ja raha tha ke Abu-Sufiyaan aur Budail bin Warqaa ko guftgu kartey suna . maine kaha : aey Abu-Hanzala ! ( ye Hazrat Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat hai) usney meri aawaz pehchan li aur kaha : Abul-Fazal? (ye Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ki kunniyat hai) maine kaha : haan . usney kaha : kya hua ? merey maa baap tujh par fidaa . maine kaha : ye Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) hain aur log bhi aap ke sath hain. usney puchha : to ab kya heela (bahana) hai? chunanche Abu-Sufiyaan merey peechhey khachchar par baith gaya aur uska doosra sathi wapis chala gaya. jab subah hui to main usey lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur usney Islam qubul kar liya . maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Abu-Sufiyaan aisa aadmi hai jisey fakhr aur badai pasand hai to aap uskey liye koi chiz khas farma den . aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' haan , jo shakhs Abu-Sufiyaan ke ghar mein dakhil ho jaey usey aman hai, jo shakhs apney ghar ka darwaza band kar ley usey aman hai, aur jo masjid mein dakhil ho jaey usey aman hai. ''Hazrat Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya : phir log apney gharon aur masjid mein bikhar gaey."
3023,Janab Wahab bin Munabba (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : maine Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha ke kya Fateh Makka ke moqe par musalmanon ne koi ghanimat hasil ki thi ? unhoney kaha : nahin.
3024,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) jab makkey mein dakhil huey to Hazrat Zuber bin Awam , Abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah aur Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ko ghud sawaron ka ameer banaya. aapney Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se farmaya : ''ansaar ko bulao.'' ( wo jama ho gaey to ( un se farmaya : ''tum log ye raasta lo aur jo bhi tumharey samney sar uthaney ki koshish karey usey silaa do ( jo bhi aslaha se muqabla karey usko qatl kar do).'' chunanche eik manadi ne aelan kiya : aaj ke baad Quraish nahin. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs apney ghar mein dakhil ho jaey usey aman hai aur jo hathiyar phenk dey usey aman hai.'' Quraish ke badon ne Kaaba ka rukh kiya aur us mein ja dakhil huey aur wo un se khacha-khach bhar gaya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Baitullah ka tawaf kiya aur maqame Ibrahim ke peechhey Namaz padhi phir Kaabe ke darwazey ki chaukhat pakad kar khadey ho gaey to wo log nikal aaye aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se Islam par baiat ki. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : maine Imam Ahmed bin Hanbal (Rahimahullah) se suna ke eik aadmi ne un se sawal kiya tha ke aaya Makka bazor quwwat (jang sey) Fateh hua tha? to unhoney kaha : jo bhi ho tumhen iska kya nuqsan hai? usney kaha : kya suleh hui thi ? unhoney farmaya : nahin."
3025,"Hazrat Wahab kehtey hain ke maine Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) se qabeela saqeef ki baiat ka haal puchha to unhoney kaha : un logon ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath shart ki thi ke wo sadqa dengey na jihad karengey. Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se baad mein suna, aap farmatey they : ''ye log jab musalman ho jaeyngey to sadqa dengey aur jihad bhi karengey. (jab Islam ke baarey mein unhen sharah sadr ho jaeyga to sab kaam karengey.'')"
3026,"Hazrat Usman bin Abi Al-Aas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke qabeela saqeef ka wafad jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to aapney unhen masjid ( nabwi ( mein thehraya taake ye unke dilon ko ziyada naram karney ka baais ho, chunanche un logon ne ye shart ki ke unhen jihad ke liye nahin bulaya jaeyga , na un se sadqaat liye jaengey aur na ye log Namaz padhengey . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye to ho sakta hai ke tumhen jihad ke liye na bulaya jaey ya sadqaat na liye jaeyn magar is deen mein koi khair nahin jis mein rukoo ( Namaz ( na ho.''"
3027,"Hazrat Aamir bin Shehar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apni nabuwat ka aelan kiya to qabeela hamdaan ke logon ne mujh se kaha : kya tum us shakhs (yani Muhammad Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) (ke paas ja kar hamarey mutalliq guftgu kar saktey ho? jis chiz par tum razi ho jaogey ham usey qubul kar lengey aur jisey tum napasand karogey ham bhi usey napasand karengey . maine kaha : haan . chunanche main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua to mujhey aap ka maamla pasand aaya aur meri qom ne Islam qubul kar liya . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Umair Zi-Murran ke taraf ye khat likha .) hua ye tha ke) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Malik bin Muraara Rahaawi ko tamam ehale Yamen ki taraf apna numaainda bana kar bheja tha. isliye eik shakhs Ak-Zoo-Khaiwan ne Islam qubul kar liya to usey kaha gaya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein jao aur aap se apni basti aur maal ke liye aman nama hasil kar lo . chunanche wo aap ki khidmat mein aaya to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usko ye tehreer likh di : ''( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( : Muhammad Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf se Ak-Zoo-Khaiwan ke liye ye tehreer hai ke agar ye sachcha ho to isey uski zameen , maal aur ghulamon ke baarey mein aman hasil hai, uskey liye Allah ka zimma hai aur Allah ke Rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka zimma hai. aur ye tehreer Khalid bin Saeed bin al-Aas ne qalam-band ki''."
3028,"Hazrat Abyaz bin Hammal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sadqe ke baarey mein baat cheet ki jabke wo wafad lekar aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaye they, to aapney farmaya : ''Sabaa ke bhai ! sadqe ki adaegi to zaroori hai.'' usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamari kaasht sirf kapaas ki hai aur qom sabaa ab titar bitar ho chuki hai aur marib ke maqam par thodey log muqeem hain. chunanche usney Allah ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suleh kar li ke wo log yani jo sabaa ke baqiya aur marib par muqeem hain salaana sattar jodey kapdey ke barabar muaafiri kapdey ki qeemat dengey . aur phir ye log Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat tak ye ada kartey rahey. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki wafat ke baad wahan ke aamilon ne unki taraf se kiya gaya wo ehad tod diya jo ke Abyaz bin Hammal (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se sattar jodon ki adaegi ka kar rakha tha. to Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ne dobara usey isi kaifiyat par lauta diya jis par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki zindagi mein tha yahan tak ke Hazrat Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ki wafat ho gaee . unki wafat ke baad ye ehad toot gaya aur) maroof andaz mein) sadqa liya janey laga."
3029,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne teen baaton ki wasiyat farmaee thi : mushrikon ko jazeera arab se nikal dena aur wufood se isi tarah bartao kartey rehna jaisey ke main kya karta hun aur teesri baat ke baarey mein Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne ya to ye kaha ke aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) khamosh rahey they ya ye kaha ke main (hi) bhool gaya hun. Humaidi ne Sufiyan se riwayat kiya ke Sulaiman ne kaha : mujhey nahin maloom ke Saeed bin Jubair ne teesri baat zikr ki thi to main bhool gaya hun ya wo ( ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) ( hi khamosh rahey they.
3030,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne Hazrat umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) se bayan kiya ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : ''main yahudiyon aur esaiyon ko jazeera arab se bil-zaroor nikal kar rahunga , main is mein musalmanon ke siwa kisi aur ko nahin chhodun ga.''"
3031,"Hazrat Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) , Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) se naqal kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya. aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya. pehli hadees ziyada mukammal hai."
3032,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''eik mulk ( arab ( mein do qibley nahin ho saktey.''"
3033,Janab Saeed bin Abdul-Azeez (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke jazeera arab se murad ( wo ilaaqa hai) jo Wadiyul-Qura se intihaaye Yamen tak aur dusri janib hudood Iraq se lekar samandar tak hai.
3034,Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ( ba-sanad Haris bin Miskeen ( bayan kartey hain ke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne ehale najraan ko jala watan kar diya lekin wo teemaa se nahin nikaley gaey kyonkey ye arab ki hudood mein nahin hai. aur wadi (al-quraa) ke yahudiyon ko bhi mera khayal hai ke nahin nikala gaya tha kyonkey unhoney isey arab ka ilaaqa na samjha . ibne Sarah ki sanad se riwayat hai ke Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) ne bayan kiya : Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne najraan aur fidak ke yahood ko jala watan kiya tha. ( kyonkey ye ilaqey jazeerae-Arab mein shumar hotey they.)
3035,Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kiya ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''(eik waqt aaney wala hai ke) Iraq apney (khiraaj ke) qafeez aur dirham rok lega aur Shaam apney mudd aur Dinar deney band kar dega aur Misr apney irdab aur dinaaron ki adaegi rok dega aur phir tum udhar hi lot jaogey jahan se ibtida (shuruat) ki thi. Zuhair ne isey teen baar dohra kar kaha : is par Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) ka gosht aur khoon gawah hai.''
3036,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jis basti mein tum aao aur wahan iqaamat ikhtiyar kar lo to us mein tumhara hissa hai (yani jo suleh se Fateh ho to fai mein tumhara hissey maroof hai) aur jo basti Allah aur uskey Rasool ki nafarmani karey to uska khums ( paanchwan hissey ( Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye hai, phir ye tumharey liye hai.''"
3037,"Janab Aasim bin umr (Rahimahullah) Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se marfooan aur Janab Usman bin Abi Sulaiman (Rahimahullah) se moqufan riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (aur kuchh doosrey Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ( ko dauma ke badshah Akeedar ki taraf rawana kiya, to unhoney isey pakad liya aur) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas ( ley aaye . to aapney uska khoon maaf kar diya aur jiziya ki adaegi par suleh kar li ."
3038,Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jab unhen Yamen ki taraf rawana kiya to unko hukm diya ke her baligh se eik Dinar ya uskey barabar muaafiri kapda wasul karen. ye kapda usi ilaqey mein buna jata tha.
3039,Masruq ne Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala riwayat ke ham-maani riwayat bayan ki .
3040,"Ziyad bin Hudair (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai ke Hazrat Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ne farmaya : agar main zinda raha to har soorat bano taghlab ke esaiyon se sakht jang karunga aur unki auladon ko qaid karunga , bila-shuba unke aur Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke darmiyan honey wala muahida maine hi tehreer kiya tha ke ye log apni auladon ko esai nahin banaeyn gey . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : ye hadees munkar hai. (yani intehai zaeef hai) Imam Ahmed (Rahimahullah) ke mutalliq mujhey maloom hua hai ke wo is hadees ko munkir tasawwur kartey they. Janab Abu-Ali  (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne dusri baar jab apni ye kitab talaba ke samney padhi to is hadees ki qirat hi nahin ki thi."
3041,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ehale najraan se ye muahida kiya tha ke wo do hazar hulley ( kapdon ke jodey ( ada kiya karengey . aadhey maah safar mein aur aadhey rajab mein . iske alawa tees zirhen , tees ghodey , tees oont aur har qism ka aslaha jo jang mein istimal hota hai tees tees ki tadaad mein aariyatan diya karengey aur musalman in chizon ke wapis kerney tak unke zaamin hongey. ( ye udhar us waqt li jaeygi ( jab Yamen mein koi fasad ya ghadr hua (aur unki zarurat padi .) aur) unke sath ehad tha ke) unka koi Maabad nahin giraya jaeyga , kisi paadri ko nahin nikala jaeyga aur unke deen mein koi mudaakhlat nahin ki jaeygi jab tak ke ye deen mein koi naee baat na nikalen aur sood na khaeyn .) raawi hadees ( Ismael (bin Abdur-Rehman Qarshi Suddi) ne kaha : chunanche un logon ne sood khaya . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : jab wo koi shart toden gey to ye deen mein naee baat nikalna hoga."
3042,Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke jab ehale Faaris ka Nabi faut ho gaya to iblees ne unhen majoosiyat ( aatish parasti) par laga diya.
3043,"Janab Abu-Sha'saa (Jabir bin Zayed (Rahimahullah) ( ne kaha : main Juz bin Muawiya ka kaatib ( secretery ( tha. aur ye Janab Ahnaf bin Qais ke chacha they, (is beech mein) Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki shahadat se eik saal pehley hamarey paas un ( Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu)) ka eik khat aaya . us mein tha : her jadugar ko qatl kar do aur majusiyon mein se jis kisi ne apni mahram aurat se nikah kiya ho un mein tafriq kara do aur unhen ( khaney ke waqt ( gungunaaney se mana kar do . chunanche ham ne eik din teen jaadugarniyon ko qatl kiya aur kitabullah ke mutabiq jis kisi ne apni mahram aurat se nikah kar rakha tha un mein judai kara di. aur) Juz bin Muawiya ne ( bahut sa khana tayyar karwaya aur phir unhen dawat di aur is dauran mein talwaar apni raan par rakh li . chunanche un logon ne khana khaya magar gungunaaey nahin. aur un logon ne eik khachchar ya do khachcharon ke bojh barabar chaandi un ( Juz bin Muawiya (ke samney dal di aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) majusiyon se jiziya leney ke qaail na they yahan tak ke Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne gawahi di ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hijr ke majusiyon se jiziya liya tha."
3044,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se marwi (bayan) hai ke hal bahreen ke) asbazi ( logon ka eik aadmi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya, ye log ehale hijr ke majusi they, ye aadmi kaee din Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein thehra raha . phir jab wapis honey laga to maine us se puchha : tumharey baarey mein Allah aur uskey Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne kya faisla kiya hai? usney kaha : bahut bura faisla . maine kaha : khamosh (yani Allah aur Rasool ka faisla bura nahin ho sakta. ( kehney laga : ( faisla ye hai ke) ya to Islam qubul kar lun ya qatl ho jaun . raawi ne kaha : Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne un se jiziya lena qubul kiya tha. Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) kehtey hain ke logon ne Hazrat Abdur-Rehman bin Auf (Raziallahu anhu) ki baat ley li hai aur meri baat chhod di hai jo maine is asbazi se suni thi."
3045,"Hazrat Hisham bin Hakim bin Hizam (Raziallahu Anhuma) ne hims ke wali ko dekha ke usney kaee qibtiyon ko jiziya ada na kar sakney ki badle mein dhoop mein khada kiya hua tha. unhoney kaha : ye kya hai? maine to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna hai, aap farmatey they : ''jo log duniya mein doosron ko azab detey hain Allah taala unhen azab dega.''"
3046,Harab bin Ubaidullah (Rahimahullah) apney naana ( umr Saqafi ( se aur wo apney walid se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''daswaan hissey (jiziya aur tax) yahudiyon aur esaiyon par hai aur musalman par koi daswaan nahin hai.''
3047,Harab bin Ubaidullah (Rahimahullah) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se riwayat kartey hain aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya aur is riwayat mein lafz ( عشور ( ki bajaey ( khiraaj ( hai.
3048,"Janab Ata , Bakr bin Waiel ke eik aadmi se aur wo apney mamu se naqal kartey hain ke maine kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! kya main apni qom se daswaan hissey liya karun? aapney farmaya : ''ye daswaan hissey yahudiyon aur esaiyon par hai.''"
3049,"Harab bin Ubaidullah bin Umair Saqafi apney dada se riwayat kartey hain jo ke bano taghlab se they, unhoney kaha : main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aaya aur Islam qubul kiya, aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mujhey Islam ke mutalliq samjhaya , aur mujhey bataya ke main apni qom ke musalmanon se kis tarah se sadqa wasul kiya karun. phir main aap ke paas dobara aaya to maine arz kiya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! aapney jo kuchh taaleem farmaee thi maine usey yaad kar liya hai siwaye sadqa ke , to kya main un se daswaan hissey liya karun? aapney farmaya : ''nahin, daswaan hissey to esaiyon aur yahudiyon par hota hai.''"
3050,"Hazrat Irbaz bin Saariya Sulmee (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke ham Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath khaibar mein utrey aur aap ke sath deegar Sahaba bhi they. khaibar ka raees eik sarkash (aur ( naa-pasandida aadmi tha. wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaya aur kaha : aey Muhammad ! kya tumharey liye jayez hai ke hamarey gadhon ko zibeh kar dalo , hamarey phal kha jao aur hamari aurton ko peeto ? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ( ye sun kar) ghussay huey aur farmaya : ''aey ibne Auf ! apney ghodey par Sawar ho aur manadi kar do ke khabrdar ! jannat sirf sahibe-emaan hi ke liye halal hai aur ye ke Namaz ke liye ikhattey ho jao .'' chunanche Sahaba kiram (Raziallahu Allahu Anhum) ikhattey ho gaey to aapney unhen Namaz padhaai , phir khadey huey aur farmaya : ''kya tum mein se koi apney takht par takiye par tek lagaey ye guman karta hai ke Allah taala ne sirf wohi kuchh haram thehraya hai jo is Quran mein hai. khabrdar ! be-shak maine Allah ki qasam ! khoob waaz aur nasihat ki hai, kaee baaton ka hukm diya hai aur kaee se mana kiya hai aur meri baat bila-shuba Quran hi ki misl (jaisi) hai ya us se badh kar) mufassal / tafseeli) hai, Allah taala ne tumharey liye halal nahin kiya ke bila ijazat ehle-kitab ke gharon mein dakhil ho jao ya unki aurton ko maaro ya unke phal kha jao, jabkey wo tumhen apney zimmey ka wajib ada kar rahey hon.''"
3051,"juhaina ( qabiley (ke eik shakhs se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' shayad ke tum eik qom se qitaal karogey aur un par ghalib aa jaogey , to wo apni janen aur apni auladen bachaney ke liye apney maal pesh karengey . Saeed (bin Mansoor) ne apni hadees mein ye izafa bayan kya : ''phir wo tum se musaalihat kar lengey.'' phir dono raawi hadees ke agley alfaz bayan kerney mein muttafiq hain, to tum us se ziyada leney ki koshish na karna kyonkey ye tumharey liye jayez na hoga.''"
3052,"Safwan bin Sulaim ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke bahut-sey Sahaba ke beton se riwayat ki, wo apney qaribi baap-dadon se riwayat kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khabrdar! jis kisi ne kisi ehad waley (zimmi) par zulm kya ya uske andar kami nikali ki (yani uskey haq mein kami ki) ya uski himmat se badh kar usey kisi baat ka mukallaf kya ya uski dili razamandi ke baghair koi chiz li to qiyamat ke roz mein uski taraf se jhagda karunga.''"
3053,"Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''musalman par jiziya nahin.''"
3054,Janab Sufiyan Sauri (Rahimahullah) se uski wazahat maloom ki gaee to unhoney kaha : jab koi shakhs Islam qubul kar ley to us par jiziya nahin.
3055,"Janab Abdullah Hozni kehtey hain ke maine halb mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke muazzan Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) se mulaqat ki aur puchha : mujhey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke ikhrajat ke baarey mein bataeyn ke unki kya keyfiyat thi? unhoney kaha : aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas jo kuch hota wo merey supurd hota tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke Nabi banaey janey se lekar wafat tak main hi uska istemal karta raha. aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka mamool tha ke jab koi musalman aadmi aapke paas aata aur aap usey dekhtey ke uskey paas kapda nahin hai to aap mujhey irshad farmatey, main jata, kahin se qarz leta aur usey chadar lekar odha deta aur khana khilata yahan tak ke mujhey mushrikon mein se eik aadmi mila usney kaha : Bilal! merey paas wusat hai, pas jab qarz lena ho to mujh hi se ley liya karo. chunanche maine aisey hi kya. so eik din maine wuzu kya ke Namaz ke liye Azan kahun, dekha ke wo mushrik apney kae tajir sathiyon ke sath aa raha hai. junhi usney mujhey dekha to bola : O Habshi ! maine kaha : aray hazir hun aur wo mujhey badey burey chehrey ke sath mila aur badi sakht baaten kin . usney kaha : maloom bhi hai ke mahiney mein kitney din baqi hain? maine kaha : qarib hi hai. usney kaha : sirf chaar din baqi hain. phir main tumhen apney maal ke badley pakad ley jaunga aur bakriyan charaney par laga dunga jaisey ke to pehley charaya karta tha, mujhey is se bahut gham hua jaisey ke insanon ko hota hai yahan tak ke jab maine Isha ki Namaz padh li aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) apney ghar walon mein tashrif ley gaey, to maine mulaqat ke liye ijazat talab ki, aapney ijazat di , to maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! merey maa baap aap par qurban ! wo mushrik jis se main qarz liya karta tha usney mujhey is is tarah kaha hai. aur adaegi ke liye na aap ke paas kuch hai aur na merey paas , aur wo mujhey ruswa kerney par aamada hai. to aap mujhey ijazat den ke kisi musalman qabiley walon ke yahan bhag jaun , yahan tak ke Allah taala apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko kuch inayat farma dey jis se mera qarza ada ho jaey. chunanche main aap ke yahan se nikal kar apney ghar aaya . maine apni talwaar, thaila, joota aur dhaal apney sar ke paas rakh liye. yahan tak ke jab pehli Fajr tulu hui to maine nikal janey ka irada kya, pas achcha eik aadmi bhaagta hua merey paas aaya, usney kaha : Bilal! Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke yahan pahuncho . main chala aur aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaya. maine dekha ke chaar oontniyaan bethi hain aur un par bojh ladey huey hain. maine ijazat talab ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' khush ho ja ! Allah taala ne terey qarzey ki adaegi ka saman bhej diya hai.'' phir farmaya : ''kya to ne chaar oontniyaan bethi dekhi hain ?'' maine kaha : haan . aapney farmaya : ''ye oontniyaan aur jo un par hai wo sab tera hai. un par kapdey hain aur khaney ka saman bhi hai. ye mujhey fidak ke sardar ne hadiya bheja hai. unhen le-ley aur apna qarza ada kar .'' ( Hazrat Bilal (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ( chunanche maine aisey hi kya. . . . . . aur hadees bayan ki . . . . phir main masjid ki janib chal pada . Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) bhi masjid mein tashrif farma they. maine salam arz kya. to aapney puchha : '' us maal ka kya hua jo tujhey mila hai? ''maine arz kya : Allah ne apney Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) par jo qarza tha sab ada karwa diya hai aur kuch baqi nahin raha . aapney puchha : ''kya koi maal bacha bhi hai? ''maine kaha : ji haan . aapney farmaya : '' dekho ! mujhey uski taraf se rahat pahunchao , main us waqt tak apney kisi ehle ke paas nahin jaunga jab tak tum mujhey uski taraf se rahat nahin dey detey .'' ( taqseem nahin kar detey .) pas jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Isha padhi to mujhey bulaya aur puchha : '' us maal ka kya hua jo tujhey hasil hua hai? ''maine arz kya : wo merey hi paas hai, hamarey paas koi (zaruratmand) nahin aaya . to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne raat masjid mein guzari. aur puri hadees bayan ki . yahan tak ke jab agley din Isha ki Namaz padh chukey to mujhey bulaya aur puchha : ''us maal ka kya bana jo tujhey mila hai? ''maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! Allah ne aap ko us se rahat ata kar di hai. (zaruratmand ley gaey hain ( to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Allahu-akbar kaha aur Allah ki hamd w sana bayan ki, aapko andesha tha ke kahen us haalat mein maut na aa jaey jabke wo maal aap ke paas mojud ho. phir main aap ke peechey-peechey chala yahan tak ke aap apni azwaaj ke paas gaey aur her eik ko Assalamualaikum kaha yahan tak ke us ghar mein tashrif ley gaey jahan aapney raat guzarni thi. to ye thi wo haalat, jiska to ne mujh se sawal kya hai."
3056,"Mehmood bin Khalid ne Marwan bin Muhammad sey, unhoney Muawiya bin Salam se riwayat kya. aur mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kya. aur jahan ye aaya hai ke) ما يقضي عني * * * ( ''main bhag jata hun aur musalman qabaayel ke paas chala jata hun yahan tak ke Allah apney Rasool ko kuch inayat farma dey jis se mera qarza ada ho jaey.'' (us riwayat mein hai ke) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mujh se khamosh ho rahey aur mujhey us se badi girani hui ."
3057,"Hazrat ayaaz bin Himar (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, wo kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein bator hadiya eik oontni pesh ki to aapney puchha : ''kya tum ne Islam qubul kar liya hai?'' maine kaha : nahin. to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''mujhey mushrekin ke atiye qubul kerney se roka gaya hai.''"
3058,Hazrat Alqama bin Waael apney walid (Hazrat Waael bin Hajar (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hazre-maut ke ilaqey main eik qataa zameen unhen ata farmaya.
3059,Jaame bin Matar ne Alqama bin Waael se mazkura baala sanad se usi ke misl bayan kya.
3060,"Hazrat Amr bin Hurais (Raziallahu anhu) ka bayan hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Madina munawwara mein mujhey eik ghar inayat farmaya jisey aapney apni Qos (kaman) se naapaa aur farmaya tha : ''main tujhey aur bhi dunga, aur bhi dunga.''"
3061,Janab Rabeea bin abi Abdur-Rehman kaee eik se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Bilal bin Haris Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) ko faraa ke atraaf mein maqam qabl ki kaanein ata farmaai thin. un kanon se aaj tak siwaye Zakat ke aur kuch nahin liya jata.
3062,"Kaseer bin Abdullah bin Amr bin Auf Muzni apney walid ( Abdullah ( se wo uskey dada ( Amr bin Auf ( se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Bilal bin Haris Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) ko maqam qabl ki kaanein inayat farmaai thin , unki baalai (upri) janib , nichey ki janib aur qudus pahad ke atraaf jahan kheti ho sakti hai. kisi doosrey musalman ka haq unhen nahin diya tha. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne unhen ye tehreer di thi : '' ( بسم الله الرحمن الرحيم ( ''ye wo Atiya hai jo Allah ke Rasool Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal bin Haris Muzni ko diya hai. usey maqam qabl ki kaanein, unke baalai (upri) aur zereen hissey aur qudus pahad ke aas-paas jahan kheti ho sakti hai, usey ata ki hain aur kisi doosrey musalman ka haq nahin diya hai. Abu-Uwais ne kaha : mujhey Saur bin Zaid ne b-waasta Ikrima Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se usi ke misl riwayat kya."
3063,"( Is-haq bin Ibrahim ( Hunaini (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke maine Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka khat ( Bilal bin Haris ki) jaagir ke mutalliq kaee baar padha hai. Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) ne kaha : hamen kaee eik ne Husain bin Muhammad se hadees sunai , unhoney kaha : hamen Abu-Uwais ne khabar di, usney kaha : mujhey Kaseer bin Abdullah ne apney walid se aur unhoney uskey dada sey, hadees bayan ki hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Bilal bin Haris Muzni (Raziallahu anhu) ko maqam qal ki kaanein unki uper aur nichey ki janib . . . . . raawi hadees ibne-Nazar ne maqam jaras aur zaatun-Nasb ka bhi zikr kya. . . . . . aur Jabal qudus ki wo zameen jo kaasht ke qabil hai, wo sab unhen den aur unhen kisi doosrey musalman ka haq nahin diya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey ye tehreer inayat farmaai : ''ye wo Atiya hai jo Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Bilal bin Haris Muzni ko inayat farmaya hai. usey maqam qabl ki kaanein unki uper ki janib, nichey ki janib aur qudus pahad ki zameen jo qabil kaasht hai ata ki hain, kisi doosrey musalman ka haq nahin diya hai.'' Abu-Uwais ne kaha : mujhey Saur bin Zaid ne b-waasta Ikrima , Hazrat ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu Anhuma) se unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se mazkura baala hadees ki misl riwayat kya.  ibn nazar ne ye izafa kya hai ke ye tehreer Ubai bin Kab (Raziallahu anhu) ne qalam band ki ."
3064,"Hazrat Abyaz bin hammal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke main eik wafad lekar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se namak ki kaan bator jaagir talab ki jo aapney de-di. . . . . . ibn mutawakkil kehtey hain wo kaan Maarib maqam par thi. . . . . . jab maine pusht pheri to majlis mein se eik aadmi ne kaha : kya aap ko maloom hai ke aapney usey kya dey diya hai, aapney usey na khatam honey wala daaimi pani dey diya hai. chunanche aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne usey wapis ley liya . phir maine sawal kya ke peelu ke kon se darkht gherey jaeyn ? ( apney qabzey mein liye ja saktey hain ( aapney farmaya : '' wo jinhen oonton ke paon na pahunchtey hon.'' (abadi se kafi door hon. ("
3065,"Janab Muhammad bin Hasan makhzoomi (Rahimahullah) ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke farman : ''wo jinhen oonton ke paon na pahunchtey hon. ''se murad ye hai ke aam chartey huey oont un darakhton sey, jahan tak ke unke munh pahunchtey hain, khatey hain, to tum unhen rok nahin saktey ho, albatta un se ooper ko tum apni milkiyat mein ley saktey ho."
3066,Hazrat Abyaz bin hammal (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke unhoney Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se peelu ke darakhton ko gherney (apney qabzey mein leney) ke mutalliq puchha to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' peelu ke darakhton ko ghera nahin ja sakta. '' ( doosron ko un se mana nahin kya ja sakta ( usney kaha ke wo darkht jo meri zameen ke ehatey mein aatey hon? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' peelu ke darakhton ko ghera nahin ja sakta. '' raawi hadees farj (bin Saeed ( ne ( hizaari (ke maani ye bataey hain ke wo zameen jis mein kheti ho aur uskey gird ehata bhi ho.
3067,"Hazrat sakhr (bin eila, abu-Haazim Hazli) (Raziallahu anhu)) se marwi (bayan) hai ke jab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bano Saqeef se jihad kya, to sakhr ne jab ye suna to apney shehsawaar lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki madad ke liye nikal khada hua . magar jab wahan pahuncha to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) usey fateh kiye baghair hi wapis ja chukey they. to sakhr ne us din Allah ke sath ye ehad kya aur apney zimmey liya ke jab tak ye log Allah ke Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka hukm nahin maan letey us waqt tak wo us qiley ko nahin chodega. chunanche aisey hi hua unhen na chhoda yahan tak ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka faisla manney par majboor ho gaey . chunanche sakhr ne ye khabar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki taraf likh bheji : hamd w salat ke baad, aey Allah ke Rasool! banu-Saqeef ne aap ka faisla qubul kar liya hai aur main unki taraf ja raha hun aur ye apney shehsawaron ke sath hain. chunanche Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne aelan karwaya ke Namaz ke liye jama ho jao. phir aapney (sakhr ki qom) Ahmas ke liye das duayen farmaeyn : ''aey Allah ! Ahmas ke shehsawaaron aur uskey piyadon ko barkat dey .'' phir wo qom Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas gaee aur Mughira-bin-Shoba ( Saqafi ( ne aap se baat ki aur kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! sakhr ne meri phuphi ko pakad liya hai, halanke wo us ( ehad ( mein dakhil ho chuki hai jis mein musalman dakhil huey hain (yani musalman ho chuki hai. ( pas aapney usey bulwaaya aur farmaya : ''aey sakhr! koi qom jab musalman ho jaey to wo apni jaan aur apney amwaal mehfooz bana leti hai, lihaza Mughira ko uski phuphi wapis kar do.'' chunanche usney usey wapis kar diya. sakhr ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se bano Sulaim ke pani ka sawal kya, wo Islam qubul kerney se bhag gaey they aur apna chashma chhod gaey they? usney kaha : aey Allah ke Nabi ! mujhey aur meri qom ko wahan nuzool ( utar kar usey apni tahweel mein leney ki ijazat den . aapney farmaya : '' haan .'' aur usey wahan utarney ki ijazat de-di. aur phir bano Sulaim waley Islam ley aaye aur sakhr ke paas aaye aur mutalba kya ke hamara chashma wapis kar do to usney inkar kar diya. wo log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein pahunchey, aur kaha : aey Allah ke nabi! ham ne Islam qubul kar liya hai aur ham sakhr ke paas gaey hain ke hamara chashma hamen wapis kar dey magar usney inkar kar diya hai. phir aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne sakhr ko bulaya to us se farmaya : ''aey sakhr! koi qom jab musalman ho jaey to wo apney amwaal aur apni janen mehfooz kar leti hai. tum qom ko unka chashma wapis kar do .'' usney kaha . bahut achcha, aey Allah ke nabi. (sakhr kehtey hain ke us waqt) maine dekha ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka chehra Mubarak haya ki wajeh se surkh ho ho gaya tha ke us se londi ley li gaee aur chashma bhi (halanke usney Islam aur musalmanon ko bahut faeyda pahunchaya tha. ("
3068,"sabra bin Abdul-Azeez bin Rabeea Johni apney walid se wo unke dada se riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( unke ilaqey mein) eik badey darkht ke nichey padaaw kya jahan ab masjid hai. aap wahan teen din thehrey , phir wahan se tabuk ki taraf rawana huey . aur juhaina qabeele ke logon ne aap se eik khuley maidan mein mulaqat ki thi. aapney un se puchha : '' zii Marwa '' maqam mein kon log muqeem hain ?'' unhoney kaha : juhaina ka khandan bano rifaa yahan rehta hai. aapney farmaya : ''ye zameen mein bano rifaa ke naam karta hun.'' chunanche un logon ne wo ( zameen ( aapas mein baant li . un mein se kisi ne bech di , kisi ne rakh li aur us mein mehnat mashaqqat (kaashtkaari waghera) kerney lagey. (ibne-Wahab kehtey hain ke) phir maine sabra ke walid Abdul-Azeez se is hadees ke mutalliq puchha to unhoney uska kuch hissey bayan kya aur puri hadees bayan nahin ki."
3069,Hazrat Asma binte-abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) bayan karti hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne ( unke shohar ( Zuber (bin awaam) (Raziallahu anhu) ko khajoor ka eik baagh inayat farmaya tha.
3070,"Janab Abdullah bin Hassaan anbari (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain ke mujhey meri daadi aur nani ne bayan kya jin ka naam Safiya aur Daheeba tha aur ye dono Aleeba ki betiyan . ... . aur Qeela binte-Makhrima ki le-palak thin. jo (Qeela) un dono ke baap ki daadi thi. . . . . . usney un dono ko bataya ke ham Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aaye aur merey sathi Hurais bin Hassaan jo qabeela Bakr bin Wayel ka bheja hua tha. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein aagey badha. aur apni aur apni qom ki taraf se Islam par baiat ki . phir usney kaha : aey Allah ke Rasool ! hamarey aur bano Tameem ke darmiyan dhana ka ilaaqa ( bator sarhad ( likh dijiye ke us se aagey unki taraf se hamari taraf koi na badhey , siwaye uskey ke koi musafir ho ya koi aagey janey wala ho. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey ladkey ! usey Dehna ka ilaaqa likh do.'' ( قیلہ ne bayan kya ke) jab maine dekha ke aap usko ye ilaaqa likh kar dey rahey hain to us se mujhey behad pareshani hui ( kyonkey ( wo mera watan hai aur mera ghar bhi wahin hai. maine arz kya : aey Allah ke Rasool ! usney aap se mutwassit qism ki zameen ka sawal nahin kya hai) balke umda aur nafis zameen talab ki hai) ye Dehna oont baandhney ki jagah hai (ke oont wahan se nikaltey hi nahin ya nikaley nahin jatey. kyonkey ye bahut sarsabz hai) aur bakriyon ki charaagaah hai. aur bano Tameem ki aurten aur unke bachey unke peechhey ( muqeem ( hain. to aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey ladkey ! ruk jao, us miskeen aurat ne sach kaha hai, musalman musalman ka bhai hota hai, pani aur darkht sab ke faaedey ke liye hain, fitna parwar logon ke muqabley mein unhen eik doosrey ke sath taawun karna chahiye.''"
3071,"Hazrat Ismir bin Muzris (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain ke main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se baiat ki, to aapney farmaya : ''jo kisi pani ( kunwen , chashmey ya taalaab ( par pehley pahunch jaey aur koi musalman us se pehley us tak na pahuncha ho to wo usi ka hua .'' raawi bayan kartey hain ke log daudtey huey nikley aur nishan lagatey jatey they."
3072,"Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu Anhuma) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne Hazrat Zuber (bin Awam (Raziallahu anhu)) ko jageer di jahan tak ke unka ghoda daud sakey . chunanche unhoney apna ghoda daudaayaa yahan tak ke wo khada ho gaya , to phir unhoney apna kodaa phenk diya. pas aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jahan tak unka kodaa pahuncha , unhen dey do.''"
3073,"Hazrat Saeed bin Zaid (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo shakhs kisi banjar (laawaaris) zameen ko abad karey, to wo usi ki hui . aur zalim rag ( insan ke andar doosrey ka haq maarney ka manfi jazba ya manfi jazbey ke tehat ki gaee ghaasibaana karrawai (ka koi haq nahin.'' (yani jisney zulman kisi jagah par qabza kar liya to uska haq tasleem nahin kiya ja sakta."
3074,"Janab Yahya bin Urwa apney walid se bayan kartey hain ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''jo koi banjar laawaaris zameen abad karey to wo usi ki hai.'' aur mazkura baala hadees ki misl (jaisi) bayan kiya. Urwa ne kaha : ye hadees bayan kerney waley ne mujhey bataya ke do shakhs apna eik jhagda Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein lekar aaye ke eik ne doosrey ki zameen mein khajuron ke darkht lagaey they to aapney faisla diya : ''zameen , zameen waley ki hai.'' aur darakhton waley ko hukm diya : ''apni khajuren ukhed ley.'' chunanche maine dekha ke un darakhton ki jadon par kulhaadey chalaey ja rahey they, halanke wo lambey lambey darkht ho gaey they yahan tak ke wo zameen se nikal liye gaey."
3075,"Janab ibne Is'haq ne apni sanad se mazkura baala hadees ke ham-maani bayan kiya, lekin unhoney (الذي حدثني هذا) ''jisney mujhey ye hadees bayan ki'' ke bajaey yun kaha : mujhey as-haabe-Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) mein se eik shakhs ne bayan kiya aur mera ghalib guman ye hai ke wo Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) hain. to maine us aadmi ko dekha ke wo khajuron ki jadon par (kulhaada) maar raha tha."
3076,"Janab Urwa bin Zuber (Rahimahullah) se riwayat hai, wo kehtey hain : main gawahi deta hun ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne faisla kiya tha ke zameen Allah ki hai aur bandey bhi Allah ke hain, to jisney koi banjar laawaaris zameen abad ki, to wohi uska Malik hai. hamein ye baat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se unhi logon ne bayan ki hai jinhon ne aap se namazon ke ehkam bayan kiye hain."
3077,"Hazrat Samura bin Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi ( laawaaris ( zameen par koi ehata bana liya , to wo usi ki milkiyat hai.''"
3078,"Janab Hisham (bin Urwa ( (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke) [عرق الظالم] ( '' zalim rag '' ka mafhoom ye hai ke ye koi shakhs kisi doosrey ki zameen mein darkht laga dey aur phir isi wajeh se is zameen ka muddai bin jaey. Imam Malik (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain ke) [عرق الظالم] ( se murad her wo chiz hai jo kisi se bala istehqaaq ( zulm sey) chheen li jaey, wahan kunwaan waghaira khod liya jaey ya darkht laga diye jaeyn ."
3079,"Hazrat Abu-Humaid Saaidi (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain ke main ghazwae tabuk mein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke sath tha. jab aap wadi Qurra se guzrey to dekha ke eik aurat apney baagh mein hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne apney sathiyon se farmaya : ''us baagh ke phal ka andaza lagao (ke kitna hoga ).''  Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne jo andaza lagaya wo das wasq tha. aapney us aurat se farmaya : ''jo phal hasil hua usey shumar (gintee) kar rakhna.'' phir ham tabuk pahunchey to Ela ke badshah ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko eik safed khachchar hadiya diya aur) uskey sile mein) aap (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne us ( Ela ke haakim ( ko eik munaqqash (chhapi hui) chadar inayat farmaee aur usey tehreer kar diya ke unka ilaaqa un hi ke paas rahega . phir jab ham wapis huey aur wadi Quraa se guzrey to aapney us aurat se daryaft farmaya : ''terey baagh ka phal kitna hua hai? '' usney bataya ke das wasq , yani wohi miqdaar jo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne bayan farmaee thi , tab Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' beshak mein Madina munawwara jaldi pahunchna chahta hun jo merey sath jaldi pahunchna chahta hai, to wo chal padey .'' ( baqi apni raftaar se aa jaeyn ("
3080,"Ummul-momenin Hazrat Zenab (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ka sar saaf kar rahi thin aur aap ke yahan Hazrat Usman bin Affan (Raziallahu anhu) ki ehliya aur deegar Muhajir khawatin bhi baithi thin , aurton ne apney gharon ki tangi ka shikwa kiya aur ye ke unhen ( shohar ki wafat ke baad) gharon se nikal diya jata hai, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne hukm diya : ''muhajrin ke ghar unki biwiyon ko virasat mein diye jaeyn.'' chunanche Hazrat Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) faut huey to unki zauja Madina main eik ghar ki waris bani thin ."
3081,"Hazrat Muaz (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhoney kaha : jisney apni gardan mein jiziye ka Qalada (patta) dala wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke tareeqey se bari ho gaya."
3082,"Hazrat Abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se marwi (bayan) hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' jisney kisi zameen ko uskey jiziye ke sath hasil kiya usney apni hijrat ko wapis kar diya, aur jisney kafir ki zillat ko uski gardan se utaar kar apni gardan mein dala usney Islam se pusht pher li.'' (Sanaan bin Qais ne kaha ke) Khalid bin Maadaan ne mujh se ye hadees suni to mujh se puchha : kya Shabeeb ne tumhen ye hadees bayan ki hai? maine kaha : haan . unhoney kaha : jab tum unke paas jao to unhen kehna ke mujhey ye hadees likh bhejen . chunanche unhoney wo likh di. jab main Khalid bin Maadaan se dobara mila to unhoney mujh se wo kaghaz talab kiya jo maine unhen dey diya. jab unhoney usey padha to apney qabzey ki sari zameenein chhod deen . Imam Abu-Dawud (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain raawi hadees Yazid bin khameer Al Yaznee, ye Shoba ke shagrid nahin hain."
3083,"Hazrat Sa'ab bin Jassaama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''koi charaagaah nahin, magar Allah aur uskey Rasool ke liye.'' ibne-Shahab (Rahimahullah) kehtey hain : mujhey ye baat pahunchi hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mauza naqeea' ko bator charaagaah mehfooz farmaya hua tha."
3084,Hazrat Sa'ab bin Jassaama (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne mauza naqeea' ko bataur charaagaah mehfooz kiya hua tha aur farmaya : ''(حمى) sirf Shan Wale Allah ke liye hai.''
3085,"Hazrat Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) bayan kartey hain, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : '' maale-madfun ( hasil ho to is ( mein paanchwan hissey hai.'' ( baitul-maal mein aam musalmanon ki munfa'at (fayde) ke liye dey , kyonkey ye bila mashaqqat hasil hua hai.)"
3086,Janab Hasan Basri (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain ke rikaz se murad wo maal hai jo kisi purani aabadi se dafn shuda miley.
3087,"Hazrat Zabaa binte Zuber bin Abdul-Muttalib bin Haashim (Raziallahu anha) ne bayan kiya ke Hazrat Miqdad (Raziallahu anhu) kisi kaam se Baqee Khabkhaba ki taraf gaey . to dekha ke eik choohaa eik surakh se Dinar nikal kar la raha hai aur phir wo eik eik karkey nikalta raha yahan tak ke usney sattarah Dinar nikaley . aur phir eik surkh rang ka kapda nikala aur us mein bhi Dinar tha aur is tarah wo atthaara ho gaey. wo inhen lekar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ke paas aagey aur arz kiya ke iska sadqa ley liijiye . Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''kya tum ne us surakh ki taraf apna haath badhaya tha?'' unhoney kaha : nahin, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''Allah tumhen barkat dey.''"
3088,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Amr (Raziallahu Anhuma) bayan kartey hain ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) se suna, jab ham taaif ki taraf rawana huey aur eik qabr ke paas se guzrey to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ne farmaya : ''ye Abu-Righal ki qabr hai. (ye Saqif ka jadde-aala (purvaj) aur qom Samud mein se tha) is Haram mein panah guzeen tha ke Allah ke azab se bacha rahey . jab wo is se bahir nikla to usey is maqam par wohi saza aa pahunchi jo uski qom ko aai thi , chunanche isi jagah dafn kar diya gaya. aur uski alamat ye hai ke iskey sath soney ki eik salaakh dafn ki gaee thi , agar tum isey ukhedo to usey uskey sath pa logey.''  to logon ne jaldi ki aur wo salaakh nikal laye."
